Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒数十五秒\N{\rEnglish}T-minus 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改为内部导引\N{\rEnglish}Guidance is internal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二、十一、十、九…\N{\rEnglish}Twelve, 11, 10, nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始准备点火\N{\rEnglish}Ignition sequence starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六、五、四\N{\rEnglish}Six, five, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三、二、一\N{\rEnglish}three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零，启动所有引擎\N{\rEnglish}Zero. All engines running.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿波罗11号升空\N{\rEnglish}Liftoff. We have liftoff on Apollo 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料和氧气状态稳定\N{\rEnglish}Fuel and oxygen steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶舱正常，动力正常\N{\rEnglish}Cabin holding. Power is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前高度是四哩\N{\rEnglish}Altitude, four miles now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度是每秒2195尺\N{\rEnglish}Velocity, 2, 195 feet per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷达资料正常\N{\rEnglish}Good radar data.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在高度3万5千英尺\N{\rEnglish}Altitude now, 33,500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有系统正常？\N{\rEnglish}How are you looking? All your systems go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们开始行动了抓紧了\N{\rEnglish}They're a go. Hang tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以继续减少动力了\N{\rEnglish}You're a go to continue power descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿，遇到一点乱流\N{\rEnglish}Uh, Houston, I'm getting a little fluctuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿，老鹰号资料传输失误\N{\rEnglish}And, Eagle, Houston, we got data drop-outs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离地面3尺，2.5\N{\rEnglish}Three feet down, two and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扬起一些尘土\N{\rEnglish}Picking up some dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，引擎停止\N{\rEnglish}Okay. Engine stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老鹰号已登陆\N{\rEnglish}The Eagle has landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（2011年1月12日）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（卫星修复任务）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把我从你身边拉走需要很长时间\N{\rEnglish}It's gonna take a lot to drag me away from you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一百个人或更多的人都无法做到\N{\rEnglish}There's nothing that a hundred men or more could ever do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祈愿非洲下雨\N{\rEnglish}I bless the rains down in Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会花一些时间去做我们从未做过的事情…\N{\rEnglish}Gonna take some time to do the things we never had...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“想念非洲下雨”到底是什么意思？\N{\rEnglish}What does it even mean to "miss the rains down in Africa "?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌词是：\N{\rEnglish}The lyrics are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我祈愿非洲下雨”\N{\rEnglish}"I bless the rains down in Africa."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是\N{\rEnglish}No, they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啦\N{\rEnglish}Uh, yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不合理了\N{\rEnglish}It makes even less sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问我就对了\N{\rEnglish}Well, I should know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我在婚礼上唱了这首歌\N{\rEnglish}because I karaoke'd it at my wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是没听到\N{\rEnglish}Well, I must have missed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太专心了，叱吒舞池\N{\rEnglish}I was in the zone. Tearing it up on the dance floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不会跳舞\N{\rEnglish}You can't dance to save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人说过你们斗嘴像老夫老妻吗？\N{\rEnglish}Anyone ever tell you guys you bicker like an old married couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她就是我工作上的老婆\N{\rEnglish}That's 'cause she's my work wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续工作吧，菜鸟\N{\rEnglish}Back to work, rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…也做不到\N{\rEnglish}...could ever do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想念非洲下雨\N{\rEnglish}I miss the rain down in Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你牺牲蜜月假和我们上太空\N{\rEnglish}I would like to thank you for spending your honeymoon in space with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是上太空就是去意大利\N{\rEnglish}It was either space or Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但意大利比不上这里的景致\N{\rEnglish}But Italy doesn't beat this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想念非洲下雨\N{\rEnglish}I miss the rains down in Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，我的老天\N{\rEnglish}Brian. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想念非洲下雨\N{\rEnglish}I miss the rains down in Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼？\N{\rEnglish}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马可斯！\N{\rEnglish}Marcus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救我！我快没空气了\N{\rEnglish}Help me. I 'm losing air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快没空气了\N{\rEnglish}I 'm losing air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔？福勒，听到请回答\N{\rEnglish}Jo. Fowler, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 救我！ - 马可斯！\N{\rEnglish}- Help me. - Marcus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\rEnglish}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，等我\N{\rEnglish}Okay, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马可斯？\N{\rEnglish}Marcus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马可斯，听到请回答\N{\rEnglish}Marcus, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马可斯？\N{\rEnglish}Marcus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马可斯！他妈的！\N{\rEnglish}Marcus. God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快啊\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快啊\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！马可斯…\N{\rEnglish}No. Marcus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会带你回家\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,220)}{\fs24\fade(1000,500)}月 球 陨 落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（售出）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,观众们可能记得那次事故\N{\rEnglish}Our viewers might remember the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即18个月前在例行修复卫星任务中发生的意外\N{\rEnglish}that happened during a routine satellite repair mission 18 months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天，华盛顿市的上诉法庭作出最终判决\N{\rEnglish}Today, a D.C. court of appeals handed down the final judgement...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,针对前宇航员布莱恩·哈珀控诉NASA非法解雇的案子\N{\rEnglish}on ex-astronaut Brian Harper's wrongful termination suit against NASA,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即他的前雇主\N{\rEnglish}his former employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已取得NASA内部汇报的画面\N{\rEnglish}We have obtained footage of an internal NASA debriefing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈珀宣称那次意外\N{\rEnglish}where Harper claimed that the accident
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是神秘的科技太空异象所致\N{\rEnglish}was caused by a mysterious technological space anomaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说有个“巨群”冲撞太空船？\N{\rEnglish}So, this so-called "swarm" hit the shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEnglish}Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讲第五十遍了\N{\rEnglish}for the 50th time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它冲进月球的危海\N{\rEnglish}It impacted in the Mare Crisium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福勒指挥官…\N{\rEnglish}Commander Fowler,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨石经过或太阳闪焰\N{\rEnglish}a passing meteor or a solar flare
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都可能造成这种干扰，对吧？\N{\rEnglish}could have caused that kind of disturbance, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我当时昏过去了\N{\rEnglish}As you know, I was unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是… - 是或不是？\N{\rEnglish}- but... - Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太阳闪焰会不会导致\N{\rEnglish}Can a solar flare cause
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在太空船系统上看到的干扰？\N{\rEnglish}the kind of disturbance you witnessed in the shuttle's onboard system?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概会吧\N{\rEnglish}I guess, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技术上是有可能\N{\rEnglish}technically. It could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在开玩笑吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友命丧太空\N{\rEnglish}I lost my friend up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的疏失\N{\rEnglish}Because of negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈珀曾因降落奋进号而被视为英雄\N{\rEnglish}Harper was once celebrated for his heroic landing of the Endeavour space shuttle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不顾机上设备完全停摆\N{\rEnglish}in spite of a complete meltdown of all onboard electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈珀已经没有其他的法律途径\N{\rEnglish}Harper's legal options have been exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次意外显然是人为疏失所导致\N{\rEnglish}and it's become clear that the accident was the result of human error.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的败诉让他彻底跌落神坛\N{\rEnglish}Today's loss is the final blow in this very public fall from grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，桑尼\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你非得重看一遍不可吗？\N{\rEnglish}Do you need to be watching that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？\N{\rEnglish}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外婆一定迫不及待想见到你\N{\rEnglish}Grandma is going to be so excited to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不来了，对吧？\N{\rEnglish}Dad's not coming, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸还有很多事要忙\N{\rEnglish}Your dad's got a lot going on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，所以我们才会卖了房子\N{\rEnglish}I know. That's why we lost the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他感恩节会来看你\N{\rEnglish}Maybe he'll come visit you for Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？\N{\rEnglish}Would you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想搬家\N{\rEnglish}I don't wanna move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌纽泽西州\N{\rEnglish}I hate New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（十年后）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（加州大学尔湾分校）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（物理与天文学系）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（尤金·艾洛伍教授）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈常说“事先征得许可不如事后请求原谅”\N{\rEnglish}My mum always said "it's better to beg for forgiveness than ask permission."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（加大尔湾分校，使用者登入）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨了，是红色还是蓝色？\N{\rEnglish}Oh, crap. Was that red or blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你告诉我是蓝色\N{\rEnglish}Please tell me it was blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智利国家天文台\N{\rEnglish}Observatorio Nacional de Chile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾斯特班？ - 哪位？\N{\rEnglish}- Esteban? - Si?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾洛伍教授\N{\rEnglish}It's Professor Arrowood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你登入我们的望远镜了，教授\N{\rEnglish}I see you're logging in to our telescope, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我还在追踪月球的轨道\N{\rEnglish}Oh, yeah. I'm still tracking our Moon's orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以请你把昨晚的扫描寄给我吗？\N{\rEnglish}Would you mind sending last night's scans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我给你的另一个电子信箱，不要用学校的\N{\rEnglish}Use the other e-mail I gave you though, not the school one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子\N{\rEnglish}Like always, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扫帚又被人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先这样吧\N{\rEnglish}Gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 再见 - 再见\N{\rEnglish}- Ciao. - Adios.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好\N{\rEnglish}Hola senoras.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（安琪儿餐馆）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你迟到了七分半钟\N{\rEnglish}You're seven and a half minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要申诉你\N{\rEnglish}I have to write this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好  - 嗨\N{\rEnglish}- Hello, there. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要什么？\N{\rEnglish}What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要一份特餐\N{\rEnglish}I'd like a Pastrami Madness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外我想请问你\N{\rEnglish}and I would also like to ask you, dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特餐是搭配什么酱？\N{\rEnglish}what sauces do you serve with the pastrami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我们有烤肉酱\N{\rEnglish}Oh, yeah. We've got barbecue,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜂蜜芥末酱\N{\rEnglish}honey mustard,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田园沙拉酱…\N{\rEnglish}ranch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（轨道距离）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么？\N{\rEnglish}What the fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一种是什么？\N{\rEnglish}What was the... The last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一份特餐马上好\N{\rEnglish}One Madness coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作时严禁使用手机\N{\rEnglish}We have a strict no phone policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以休息十分钟吗？\N{\rEnglish}Can I take my 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？\N{\rEnglish}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是KC·豪斯曼博士\N{\rEnglish}My name is Dr. KC Houseman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有可能找到人类史上最重要的发现\N{\rEnglish}and I've uncovered what might be the most important discovery in human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你马上转接NASA局长\N{\rEnglish}I need you to patch me through to the director of NASA immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（航空航天局）\N亲爱的，我是卖T恤和玩具的\N{\rEnglish}Honey, I sell T-shirts and toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮你转接客服部\N{\rEnglish}I can patch you through to customer service.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等\N{\rEnglish}Please hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑咖啡，两块糖\N{\rEnglish}Black, two sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会读心啊，谢谢\N{\rEnglish}Oh, you read my mind. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么早起床？\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想问你同一个问题\N{\rEnglish}I could ask you the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都好吗？\N{\rEnglish}Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会好的\N{\rEnglish}Will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会回来吃晚饭\N{\rEnglish}So I'm gonna be home by dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没回来\N{\rEnglish}If I'm not,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得叫吉米写作业、洗澡…\N{\rEnglish}make sure Jimmy does his homework, has a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心太多了\N{\rEnglish}You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我在一切搞定\N{\rEnglish}I've got everything under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再聊\N{\rEnglish}Talk soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（约翰逊航天中心）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（德克萨斯州 休斯顿）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，不要这么多人同时说话\N{\rEnglish}Okay, don't everybody speak at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球轨道改变了\N{\rEnglish}The Moon's orbit has shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轨道半径正在缩减中\N{\rEnglish}Its orbital radius is decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能\N{\rEnglish}Well, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是这么想\N{\rEnglish}We thought the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以检查了数字又再三确认资料\N{\rEnglish}so we ran the numbers and triple-checked our data.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球绕着地球转了几十亿年\N{\rEnglish}So, the Moon's been orbiting around the Earth for billions of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你跟我说它改变轨道？\N{\rEnglish}and now you're telling me it's changed its course?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是幼儿园，说吧\N{\rEnglish}This isn't kindergarten, speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啦，在最近的绕行轨道上\N{\rEnglish}Right, uh, yes. So, on its last orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球探测器侦测到异常的东西\N{\rEnglish}our Lunar Reconnaissance Probe picked up something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？\N{\rEnglish}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前不知道\N{\rEnglish}We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已对它内部散发的气体光谱进行光度测定\N{\rEnglish}We have photometric measurements of gaseous spectra being emitted from inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？\N{\rEnglish}Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危海\N{\rEnglish}Mare Crisium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我告诉你多少遍？\N{\rEnglish}How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要马上告诉福勒副局长\N{\rEnglish}I need to speak to Deputy Director Fowler immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这很紧急\N{\rEnglish}But this is urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道限制令是怎么规定的\N{\rEnglish}I understand how a restraining order works,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你们NASA不听我说\N{\rEnglish}but if you people at NASA won't listen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么…\N{\rEnglish}how am I supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（SpaceX太空探索技术公司）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃隆会怎么做？\N{\rEnglish}What would Elon do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛德林啊\N{\rEnglish}Oh, Fuzz Aldrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讲过多少次要尿在砂盆里？\N{\rEnglish}How many times have I told you to use the litter box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N{\rEnglish}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“宇航员节”\N{\rEnglish}"Astronaut Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天\N{\rEnglish}This is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛毛\N{\rEnglish}Fuzz,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是天才！\N{\rEnglish}you're a damn genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚点给你抓背奖励\N{\rEnglish}Extra back scratches later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们老师说你是爽约的废物\N{\rEnglish}Our teacher said you're a washed up no-show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她去找人投诉\N{\rEnglish}She's complaining to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来真的不像宇航员\N{\rEnglish}You really don't look like an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是来教我们太空的事吗？\N{\rEnglish}Well, are you going to teach us about space or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门！你三个月没缴房租了！\N{\rEnglish}Open the goddamn door. You're three months late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠！\N{\rEnglish}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听得见你在里面\N{\rEnglish}I can hear you in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 靠！ - 布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}- Oh, shit. - Brian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说白了，月球是个巨型结构\N{\rEnglish}To put it bluntly, the Moon is a megastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们懂吗？\N{\rEnglish}Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大型人造结构\N{\rEnglish}Huge and artificial!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个不可思议结构的制造者一定觉得我们是可悲的物种\N{\rEnglish}Whoever built this incredible thing must think we're a pathetic species.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但千万别让我讲起日蚀\N{\rEnglish}But don't even get me started on eclipses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日蚀之所以发生是因为\N{\rEnglish}They're only possible because
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球比太阳小了四百倍\N{\rEnglish}the Moon is exactly 400 times smaller than the Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又更靠近地球四百倍\N{\rEnglish}and exactly 400 times closer to the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人知道为什么吗？\N{\rEnglish}Anyone know how that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为月球是巨型结构？\N{\rEnglish}'Cause the Moon's a megastructure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，有人在专心听\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, someone's paying attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你们一件事\N{\rEnglish}Let me tell you kids something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿波罗12号的空油箱落地时\N{\rEnglish}When Apollo 12 dropped their empty fuel tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞击让月球发出像钟的声音\N{\rEnglish}the impact made the Moon ring like a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响了好几个小时\N{\rEnglish}It rang for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道为什么吗？\N{\rEnglish}And do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为月球是空心的\N{\rEnglish}Because the damn Moon is hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试着接受吧\N{\rEnglish}Put that in your pipe and smoke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\rEnglish}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是布莱恩·哈珀\N{\rEnglish}I'm Brian Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天受邀来演讲\N{\rEnglish}I'm supposed to be speaking here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是巨型结构学家KC·豪斯曼\N{\rEnglish}I'm Dr. KC Houseman, megastructurist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸会\N{\rEnglish}It's a real honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，你是谁？\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个惊天动地的大发现\N{\rEnglish}I've made a shocking discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要你马上帮我联络NASA\N{\rEnglish}I need you to get me in touch with NASA immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和NASA目前没再往来了\N{\rEnglish}Well, NASA and I aren't really on speaking terms these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们会的\N{\rEnglish}Well, that will change
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你告诉他们月球脱离轨道之后\N{\rEnglish}when you tell them that the Moon is out of orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？\N{\rEnglish}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友们，我先去解决这件事\N{\rEnglish}Hey, kids, I'm gonna go get this all sorted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上回来\N{\rEnglish}Be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这份资料\N{\rEnglish}Look at the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天体不会一夜之间离开运行轨道\N{\rEnglish}A natural body does not change its orbit overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啦，我的身体正在离开你\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, well, my natural body is walking away from you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球的动力来源一定出问题了\N{\rEnglish}There must be something wrong with the Moon's power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，一定是这样\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, that must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会相信我\N{\rEnglish}I knew you'd believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都当我是个神经病\N{\rEnglish}People usually think I'm some kind of crackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位，我要送这个冒充我\N{\rEnglish}Hey, fellas, I need this guy escorted off the premises
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骚扰一群学童的人离开这里\N{\rEnglish}for impersonating me and creeping out a bunch of school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有冒充你\N{\rEnglish}I was not impersonating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生，请你跟我们走\N{\rEnglish}Sir, I'm going to have to ask you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我已经够忙了\N{\rEnglish}Sorry, man. I got enough on my plate without
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没空理说月球脱离轨道的神经病\N{\rEnglish}some crazy guy thinking the Moon's out of orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不是神经病  -好吧\N{\rEnglish}- I'm not crazy! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看\N{\rEnglish}Read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，我走\N{\rEnglish}All right, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（强制迁离通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（布兰达）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是拨错号码？\N{\rEnglish}Is this a butt dial?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快看第16频道\N{\rEnglish}Put on channel 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我们在冷战\N{\rEnglish}Well, I thought we weren 't speaking anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有在看吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少闯了两个红灯的两名嫌犯…\N{\rEnglish}The two suspects who have rolled through at least two red lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个白痴以为能甩掉警察\N{\rEnglish}looks like some idiot tried to outrun the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，那个白痴是你儿子\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. That idiot is your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼又没有车，那辆野马我还在修\N{\rEnglish}Sonny doesn't even have a car. I'm still fixing up the Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆送他一辆车当生日礼物\N{\rEnglish}Tom gave him one for his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车子停下来了，是一部昂贵的跑车\N{\rEnglish}The car has stopped. It's an expensive sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两名20出头的年轻人…\N{\rEnglish}Two young men that appear to be in their 20s...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有在看吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶警方拘留了他们\N{\rEnglish}LAPD have them in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两人出来兜风，结果要睡在警局了\N{\rEnglish}Out for a joy ride and this day is not going to end well for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，又是一场飞车追逐…\N{\rEnglish}There you have it. Another high-speed car chase...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个案子是桑尼·哈珀\N{\rEnglish}Next case, Sonny Neil Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这上面说你刚满18岁\N{\rEnglish}It says here you just turned 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾，法律认定你是成年人了\N{\rEnglish}Unfortunately, that makes you an adult in the eyes of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不说句话吗？\N{\rEnglish}Aren't you gonna say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的行为莽撞\N{\rEnglish}Because of the reckless nature of your actions
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被捕时身上持有的毒品量…\N{\rEnglish}and the amount of illegal substances present at the time of your arrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，庭上，那些毒品不是他的，是他朋友的\N{\rEnglish}No, Your Honor. Those drugs weren't his. They were just his buddy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们要去演唱会  - 法庭上安静\N{\rEnglish}- They were on their way to a concert. - Quiet in my court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是害怕，所以才会逃跑\N{\rEnglish}Well, he just got scared. That's why he took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，够了，法警！\N{\rEnglish}All right, that's it. Bailiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庭上，请原谅我委托人父亲的言行\N{\rEnglish}Your Honor, excuse the actions of my client's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管保释金多少，我们马上付钱\N{\rEnglish}We're prepared to pay whatever the ball is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱不是问题\N{\rEnglish}Money's no object.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那被告就有逃亡之虞了\N{\rEnglish}Well, I guess that makes the defendant a flight risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庭上，我们绝对无意冒犯\N{\rEnglish}Your Honor, we do not mean to offend the court in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场保释听证会延到下周\N{\rEnglish}I'm postponing this bail hearing till next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法警，把哈珀先生带走\N{\rEnglish}Bailiff, remove Mr. Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，你不能…不要听他的\N{\rEnglish}Wait. You can't... Don't listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能把他关一个星期，我求求你\N{\rEnglish}You can't put him in jail for a week. Please, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼，我会保你出来的\N{\rEnglish}Sonny, I'm gonna get you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要最划算的服务\N{\rEnglish}If you're looking for the deal of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就来雷克萨斯汽车找汤姆·罗培兹\N{\rEnglish}come to Tom Lopez Lexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里你不只是个顾客\N{\rEnglish}where you're not just a customer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们待你如同家人\N{\rEnglish}we treat you like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道法庭是怎么运作的吗？\N{\rEnglish}Do you have any idea how a courtroom operates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的律师什么也没做\N{\rEnglish}Your lawyer was doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你懂得比我的律师更多\N{\rEnglish}Oh, so you know better than my lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的律师费是五万美元耶！\N{\rEnglish}who's on a $50,000 retainer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为钱不是问题，汤姆\N{\rEnglish}I thought money was no object, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没钱就有问题了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, no, no, no. It is when you don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，干得好\N{\rEnglish}Nice move, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼现在有逃亡之虞了\N{\rEnglish}Sonny's now a flight risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啦\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真够夸张，不可思议\N{\rEnglish}This guy's unbelievable. Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，大家都冷静\N{\rEnglish}All right, everyone, just cool it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 到底怎么回事？  - 怎么回事？\N{\rEnglish}- Now, what the hell happened? - Oh, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩管不住嘴就说了不该说的话\N{\rEnglish}When Brian had to open his big mouth, he had a little speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天，下地狱吧，汤姆\N{\rEnglish}Oh, my God. Go to hell, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，你知道吗？\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你滚到外太空，离我们远点\N{\rEnglish}And you go to outer space, far away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想救出桑尼\N{\rEnglish}We're all just trying to help Sonny right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩想救桑尼？几时的事？\N{\rEnglish}Oh, wait, Brian's trying to help Sonny? Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布兰达，你是看上这蠢货哪一点？\N{\rEnglish}Brenda, honestly, what do you see in this schmuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自以为了不起吗？\N{\rEnglish}Oh, you're a big man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么发生的？他为何不在南加大？\N{\rEnglish}How did this happen? Why wasn't he at USC?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你送了他新公寓他就搬出去了\N{\rEnglish}He moved out when you got him that new apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去问他啊\N{\rEnglish}So ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他最近都不回我电话了\N{\rEnglish}He barely returns my calls anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对我也一样啦\N{\rEnglish}Welcome to the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，是你吗？\N{\rEnglish}Oh, KC, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈，迷迭香\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Mum. Rosmarinus officinalis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有研究发现闻迷迭香\N{\rEnglish}A few studies have found that smelling rosemary
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以改善短期记忆\N{\rEnglish}can improve your short-term memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Oh, that's lovely, dear. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，妈，让我来\N{\rEnglish}Oh, no, no, no, Mum. Let me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉怎样？\N{\rEnglish}So, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好极了\N{\rEnglish}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直讲我的事\N{\rEnglish}But enough about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人都知道\N{\rEnglish}Everybody here knows that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子是在NASA工作的天才\N{\rEnglish}my son is a genius working at NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈，我是个无名小卒\N{\rEnglish}I'm a nobody, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你很了不起\N{\rEnglish}Well, you're somebody to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有个发现，但不重要啦\N{\rEnglish}I actually did make a discovery. But it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人要听我说\N{\rEnglish}No one will listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼他们听啊\N{\rEnglish}Then make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼他们听？\N{\rEnglish}Make them listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\rEnglish}Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是新来的吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you new here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\rEnglish}No, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是KC\N{\rEnglish}It's me. It's KC.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子\N{\rEnglish}Your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问谁能告诉我这是什么？\N{\rEnglish}Can someone tell me what the hell I'm looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球进入了椭圆轨道\N{\rEnglish}The Moon has entered an elliptical orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是？\N{\rEnglish}Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会绕着我们转三圈\N{\rEnglish}It'll circle around us three times
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后抵达一万七千公里的洛希极限\N{\rEnglish}before it reaches the Roche Limit at 17,000 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,届时如城市般大小的月球碎片\N{\rEnglish}At that point, city-sized pieces of Moon debris
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会朝我们飞撒而来\N{\rEnglish}will rain down on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是三个月后？\N{\rEnglish}So we have three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不完全正确\N{\rEnglish}Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着月球愈靠近我们\N{\rEnglish}As the Moon moves closer to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个月的时间就会开始缩短\N{\rEnglish}our months will begin to shorten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们估计的时间约为三个星期\N{\rEnglish}We've estimated a timeline of roughly three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能还不到\N{\rEnglish}Maybe less than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚收到几张新的高清扫描\N{\rEnglish}We have some new high-res scans that just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的老天\N{\rEnglish}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坑底是有个洞吗？\N{\rEnglish}Is that a hole in the crater floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们现在怎么办？\N{\rEnglish}So what are our options here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须回月球上看看\N{\rEnglish}We have to go back to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看看那里的情况\N{\rEnglish}We have to see what's going on up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要如何载人？\N{\rEnglish}How do we carry crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经找欧洲那边谈过了\N{\rEnglish}I've already talked to my contacts in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STC-62应该明天就能升空\N{\rEnglish}We can potentially get a STC-62 en route by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该？好极了\N{\rEnglish}Potentially? Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去向总统报告可能发生的事\N{\rEnglish}I'll just brief the president on a maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事不准对外声张\N{\rEnglish}In the meantime, everyone keep your mouths shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（警讯：月球偏离轨道）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可能做不到\N{\rEnglish}That might be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两分钟前消息在推特传开了\N{\rEnglish}It's, uh, trending on Twitter as of two minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你前夫找你\N{\rEnglish}It's your ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，道格\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Doug,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有点忙，什么事？\N{\rEnglish}I'm a little busy right now. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗？\N{\rEnglish}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我这是误传\N{\rEnglish}Tell me there's been some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想啊\N{\rEnglish}I wish I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但计算后是对的\N{\rEnglish}but the math actually checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是真的\N{\rEnglish}So, it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米还好吗？\N{\rEnglish}How's Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若是偶尔有见到他就会知道了\N{\rEnglish}Well, you'd know if you saw him once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要跟我吵，我常打给他\N{\rEnglish}Please don't start. I call him all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，先这样吧\N{\rEnglish}Sorry, I gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 庭上  - 我的老天\N{\rEnglish}- Your Honor. - Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来挂你电话还不够明确\N{\rEnglish}I guess hanging up wasn't clear enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只耽误你两分钟\N{\rEnglish}I just need two minutes of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你讲到门口\N{\rEnglish}You have till I reach the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一台经典摩托车和我儿子的古董野马\N{\rEnglish}I got a classic bike and my son's vintage Mustang
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以抵押，让我筹到你需要的钱\N{\rEnglish}that I can use as collateral till I get money, whatever you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想贿赂我吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you trying to bribe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法院里？\N{\rEnglish}In a courthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想救回我儿子\N{\rEnglish}I just wanna get my son back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭关闭了\N{\rEnglish}The courts are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期一会开吗？\N{\rEnglish}Will they reopen Monday?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\rEnglish}Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这话是什么意思？\N{\rEnglish}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想赶在大塞车前离开这里\N{\rEnglish}Look, I'm just trying to get the heck outta here before the traffic becomes a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 建议你也赶快走  - 突发新闻\N{\rEnglish}- I suggest you do the same. - Breaking news.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要现场直播NASA的新闻快报\N{\rEnglish}We go now live to the NASA press briefing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨论月球偏离轨道的记者会\N{\rEnglish}to discuss the Moon being out of orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天文学家最近发现月球表面有亮点\N{\rEnglish}Astronomers have noticed bright lights on the lunar surface lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道匿名爆料者的身分吗？\N{\rEnglish}Do you know the identity of the anonymous source?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位\N{\rEnglish}Everyone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信月球探测任务\N{\rEnglish}We 're confident that the lunar recon mission
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会提供解决这个问题所需的资料\N{\rEnglish}will provide the necessary data to address the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必惊慌\N{\rEnglish}There's no need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先这样\N{\rEnglish}That's all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才对全国撒了谎\N{\rEnglish}You just lied to the whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我的，你在我底下工作\N{\rEnglish}Get in line, you work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.59,0:23:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我效力于美国人民，你却欺瞒他们\N{\rEnglish}I work for the American people, and you're keeping them in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NASA想要粉饰太平\N{\rEnglish}NASA is completely downplaying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像海边的潮汐\N{\rEnglish}Imagine the tides on the coast...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涨了几百倍高，往内陆移动几百哩\N{\rEnglish}growing hundreds of times larger, moving hundreds of miles inland,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就知道目前的情况有多危急了\N{\rEnglish}then you'll get an idea of what we 're in for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:23:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持反对意见者认为你在夸大…\N{\rEnglish}Some of your harshest critics claim that you're exaggerating...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.65,0:24:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有飞西岸的航班都取消了\N{\rEnglish}All flights to the West Coast have been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还在堵车\N{\rEnglish}And I'm stuck in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉\N{\rEnglish}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往高处移动是唯一可能保命的方法\N{\rEnglish}Moving to higher ground it's the only possible chance of surviving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老婆，我们应该去亚斯本\N{\rEnglish}Honey. We should go to Aspen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.60,0:24:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那桑尼怎么办？我们不能丢下他\N{\rEnglish}What about Sonny? We can'tjust leave him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.71,0:24:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我们不会丢下他\N{\rEnglish}No, no, no. We 're not gonna leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.08,0:24:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官定了保释金，律师就会保释他\N{\rEnglish}The lawyer's gonna get him out the moment the judge sets bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再想办法送他去科罗拉多\N{\rEnglish}And I'll find a way to get him to Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去科罗拉多？\N{\rEnglish}We're going to Colorado?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.47,0:24:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，汤姆\N{\rEnglish}No. No, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.86,0:24:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,较大的地球引力\N{\rEnglish}Earth's stronger gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.51,0:24:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会完全摧毁月球，并且把成千上万的…\N{\rEnglish}will completely break the Moon apart and send thousands of...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.59,0:24:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 直径1000多米的碎片雨点般砸向地球  - 好了，Google\N{\rEnglish}-  mile-sized chunks raining down upon the planet. - Okay. Hey, Google.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.98,0:24:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关掉电视\N{\rEnglish}Turn off the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.87,0:24:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去打包行李  - 关掉电视\N{\rEnglish}- Girls, go pack. - Turning the TV off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去打包雪靴，动作快\N{\rEnglish}Girls, go pack your snow boots. Come on. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要开始为女儿们做打算\N{\rEnglish}We have to start thinking about the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.92,0:24:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我，我们不会忘了桑尼\N{\rEnglish}And trust me, we are not gonna forget about Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.76,0:24:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒数五秒\N{\rEnglish}T-minus five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四、三\N{\rEnglish}Four, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.80,0:24:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二、一\N{\rEnglish}two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.40,0:24:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点火\N{\rEnglish}Ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.48,0:24:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都在屏息以待\N{\rEnglish}The entire world is holding its collective breath
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.82,0:24:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NASA和欧洲各大太空机构的联合行动\N{\rEnglish}as the joint missions between NASA and the European Space Agencies
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.31,0:24:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要升空\N{\rEnglish}take to the skies today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.08,0:25:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各国都对于航空航天局的探月任务很乐观\N{\rEnglish}Nations remain hopeful of NA SA 's lunar mission
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.75,0:25:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民众持续大量采买和囤积物资\N{\rEnglish}as frantic shoppers continue to stockpile supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.78,0:25:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球恐慌引发大批人潮移出都会区\N{\rEnglish}as mounting Moon terror fuels the mass migration out of metropolitan areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.20,0:25:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文明社会已经沉沦了\N{\rEnglish}Civilization has already taken a serious nosedive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.04,0:25:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打家劫舍在英国各地随处可见\N{\rEnglish}Looting has become a favorite pastime in the United Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.04,0:25:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧和惊慌占据了我们的市区\N{\rEnglish}Fear and panic have overtaken our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.32,0:25:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国民警卫队拼命地想维持秩序\N{\rEnglish}The National Guard struggles to restore some kind of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.40,0:25:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持清醒吧，我的兄弟姐妹们\N{\rEnglish}Stay awake, my brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.52,0:25:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在繁星从天而坠时，要保持清醒\N{\rEnglish}As the stars fall from Heaven, stay awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.36,0:25:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些武装的宗教狂热份子\N{\rEnglish}These armed religious fanatics
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.07,0:25:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在全国各地累积了数千名信徒\N{\rEnglish}have racked up thousands of followers all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,播报其它新闻\N{\rEnglish}In other news,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.77,0:25:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知名科学家如今都在探讨\N{\rEnglish}prominent scientists are now exploring the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.73,0:25:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球是某种绕行巨型结构的可能性\N{\rEnglish}that perhaps the Moon could be some sort of orbital megastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.08,0:25:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最早是非主流天文学家常用的名词\N{\rEnglish}A term first popularized by fringe astronomers,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.48,0:25:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨型结构是指行星大小的人造物\N{\rEnglish}megastructures describe artificial planet-sized objects
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.70,0:25:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说藉由控制恒星获得动力\N{\rEnglish}said to be powered by captured stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.89,0:25:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个曾是偏激的理论如今获得了\N{\rEnglish}This once radical possibility is now gaining traction
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.67,0:25:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急欲找到答案的科学界的广泛关注\N{\rEnglish}among a scientific community desperate for answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.76,0:26:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来！双手举高！\N{\rEnglish}Come out! Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.48,0:26:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别激动\N{\rEnglish}Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.32,0:26:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是几天前的那个宇航员\N{\rEnglish}You're that astronaut guy from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.60,0:26:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心扔掉了一些很重要的文件\N{\rEnglish}I accidentally threw away some very important papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.16,0:26:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你走运，清洁员一个礼拜没来了\N{\rEnglish}Lucky for you, sanitation hasn't come by all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.88,0:26:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，算我走运\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, it's, uh, lucky for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.04,0:26:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（轨道距离）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轨道距离？\N{\rEnglish}"Orbital distance"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在找的是这个吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.59,0:26:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（KC豪斯曼博士）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.72,0:26:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位巨型结构学家…\N{\rEnglish}My fellow megastructurists,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.12,0:26:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你正在看这段影片\N{\rEnglish}if you're watching this, then you know by now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.68,0:26:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道我们麻烦大了\N{\rEnglish}a huge problem is heading our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.28,0:26:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们能解决这个问题\N{\rEnglish}and we're the only ones who can solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.72,0:26:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急召开会议，即刻在老地方见\N{\rEnglish}An emergency meeting is being called, our usual place immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.60,0:26:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶棕榈饭店，今天晚上6点\N{\rEnglish}L.A. Palm Hotel. Today. 18:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.28,0:26:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提供免费贝果\N{\rEnglish}Free bagels.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.60,0:26:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球轨道嵌入完成\N{\rEnglish}Lunar orbit insertion complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.84,0:26:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿，我们正在接近危海\N{\rEnglish}Houston, we 're approaching the Mare Crisium.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.00,0:27:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始旋转太空舱\N{\rEnglish}Initiating capsule rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.40,0:27:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEnglish}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.20,0:27:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15度\N{\rEnglish}Fifteen degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.04,0:27:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30度\N{\rEnglish}Thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.16,0:27:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,45度\N{\rEnglish}Forty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.32,0:27:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,70度\N{\rEnglish}Seventy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.62,0:27:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,90度\N{\rEnglish}Ninety.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.48,0:27:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STC-62就定位\N{\rEnglish}STC-62 in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.12,0:27:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿，看见了吗？\N{\rEnglish}Houston, you seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.72,0:27:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，看见了\N{\rEnglish}Copy, we see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.96,0:27:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备部署探测器\N{\rEnglish}Prepare to deploy the probe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.39,0:27:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEnglish}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.89,0:27:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放探测器\N{\rEnglish}Releasing probe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.28,0:27:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待第二阶段指令\N{\rEnglish}Stand by for stage two.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.16,0:27:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳定落下\N{\rEnglish}Dropping steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.87,0:27:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（洛杉矶棕榈饭店）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.20,0:27:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个平台我都有贴文\N{\rEnglish}Iposted on every platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.16,0:27:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何NASA那些白痴没看出真正的问题？\N{\rEnglish}Why don't those idiots at NASA see the real problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.76,0:27:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们显然没读过知名宇宙学家卡尔·萨根的著作\N{\rEnglish}Because they obviously haven't read famed cosmologist Carl Sagan's work,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.28,0:28:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在书里明确提到\N{\rEnglish}where he clearly states
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.52,0:28:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天然卫星不可能是空心的\N{\rEnglish}that a natural satellite cannot be a hollow object.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.04,0:28:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个我讲了很多年，豪斯曼博士\N{\rEnglish}I... I've been saying that for years, Dr. Houseman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.06,0:28:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锡吉，现在讲这个也没用吧？\N{\rEnglish}That doesn't help us now, does it, Ziggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.36,0:28:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在座都是世上最聪明又有远见的人\N{\rEnglish}This room is full of the smartest and most visionary people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.24,0:28:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都知道月球是人造结构\N{\rEnglish}We all know the Moon's a constructed object. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.60,0:28:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有办法解决\N{\rEnglish}There has to be a way to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.15,0:28:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，各位\N{\rEnglish}Come on, people,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.35,0:28:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳脱框架思考\N{\rEnglish}think outside the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.16,0:28:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯瓦尔德干的（此人枪杀了肯尼迪）\N{\rEnglish}Oswald did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.80,0:28:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了，盖瑞，现在别讲这个\N{\rEnglish}Oh, damn it, Gary. Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.16,0:28:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈珀先生？\N{\rEnglish}Mr. Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.48,0:28:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这儿？\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.96,0:28:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我犯了个大错\N{\rEnglish}Probably making a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.28,0:28:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便谈谈吗？\N{\rEnglish}Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.23,0:28:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我在这儿？\N{\rEnglish}How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.48,0:28:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的网站\N{\rEnglish}Your website.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.36,0:28:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看了我的部落格？\N{\rEnglish}You read my blog?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.44,0:28:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比任何人更早知道这件事\N{\rEnglish}You knew all this was happening before anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.08,0:28:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也比NASA更早\N{\rEnglish}Before NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.55,0:28:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道的？\N{\rEnglish}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.72,0:28:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很重要吗？\N{\rEnglish}Why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.24,0:28:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又会骂我神经病\N{\rEnglish}You're just gonna say I'm crazy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.31,0:28:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试看啊\N{\rEnglish}Try me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.88,0:28:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多年来我一直在研究遥远的行星\N{\rEnglish}Well, for years I've been studying distant planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.84,0:28:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找绕行的巨型结构 但是…\N{\rEnglish}searching for one of these orbiting megastructures. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.58,0:29:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过在这里就有一个\N{\rEnglish}I never could have imagined there'd be one right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.11,0:29:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我们自家后院\N{\rEnglish}in our own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.08,0:29:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有听过戴森球？\N{\rEnglish}Ever heard of a Dyson sphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.32,0:29:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.48,0:29:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个巨型结构都会有个坚实的外壳包住的动力核心\N{\rEnglish}Every megastructure has a rigid shell built around a power core.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.00,0:29:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是被控制住汲取能源的白矮星\N{\rEnglish}Most likely a captured white dwarf that's being harnessed for energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.04,0:29:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球内部的核心显然出了问题\N{\rEnglish}Something obviously happened to the one inside our Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.60,0:29:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会偏离轨道\N{\rEnglish}and that's why it's veering off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.56,0:29:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然还是神经病\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, still crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.84,0:29:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算相信我干嘛还来？\N{\rEnglish}Why did you come here if you're not going to believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.16,0:29:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道那种感觉\N{\rEnglish}'Cause I know what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.30,0:29:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有话想告诉别人却没人要听\N{\rEnglish}to try to tell people something and have no one listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探测器深度已达24.5公里\N{\rEnglish}Probe depth has reached 24.5 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.60,0:29:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25公里\N{\rEnglish}Twenty-five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.00,0:29:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停在25.6公里\N{\rEnglish}Holding steady at 25.6 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.96,0:29:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是停着\N{\rEnglish}Still holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.72,0:29:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 停止了吗？  - 它回来了\N{\rEnglish}- It stopped? - It's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.28,0:29:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,24公里\N{\rEnglish}Twenty-four kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.72,0:29:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20公里\N{\rEnglish}Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.58,0:29:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15公里\N{\rEnglish}Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.68,0:29:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又出问题了\N{\rEnglish}We got another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.20,0:30:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 月球轨道再次偏移  - 什么？\N{\rEnglish}- The Moon's orbit is shifting again. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.60,0:30:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在自行修正轨道\N{\rEnglish}It's correcting itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.22,0:30:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿，我们发生了机械故障\N{\rEnglish}Houston, we're experiencing some kind of malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.89,0:30:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿，听到请回答\N{\rEnglish}Houston, do you copy? Houston, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.40,0:30:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼？\N{\rEnglish}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.19,0:30:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\rEnglish}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.61,0:30:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（警告：侦测到机身受损）
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.04,0:30:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机身受损，戴头盔\N{\rEnglish}Hull breach. Helmets.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（无信号）
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.32,0:31:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新闻快报\N{\rEnglish}In breaking news,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.68,0:31:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NASA刚才修正了\N{\rEnglish}NASA has just corrected...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.25,0:31:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球坠落地球路径的最初预测\N{\rEnglish}their initial projection of the Moon's path over Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.56,0:31:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（月球轨道偏移导致美国洪灾）
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.72,0:31:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府刚才下令整个西岸大学疏散\N{\rEnglish}The governor has just ordered the mass evacuation of the entire West Coast,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.72,0:31:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建议民众紧急前往高处避难\N{\rEnglish}recommending that people urgently head to higher ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位！\N{\rEnglish}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.12,0:32:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潮水冲过来了\N{\rEnglish}The... The... The tide, it's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.20,0:32:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，我们赶快逃\N{\rEnglish}Come on. We gotta get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.56,0:32:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！\N{\rEnglish}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.04,0:32:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家上楼！快！\N{\rEnglish}Everybody, upstairs. Go! Everybody, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都起来！快点！动作快！\N{\rEnglish}Come on! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.88,0:32:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，你在干嘛？\N{\rEnglish}KC, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.32,0:32:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K·C！\N{\rEnglish}KC!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.20,0:32:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，撑住\N{\rEnglish}KC, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会游泳\N{\rEnglish}I can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.80,0:32:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豪斯曼博士！\N{\rEnglish}Dr. Houseman!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.12,0:32:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧！\N{\rEnglish}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那儿，他在那儿\N{\rEnglish}He's right there. He's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.64,0:33:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧！\N{\rEnglish}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.40,0:33:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\rEnglish}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.84,0:33:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来！\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.80,0:33:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.84,0:33:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是某种有自觉\N{\rEnglish}It's some kind of self-aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.80,0:33:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会自我复制的个体\N{\rEnglish}self-replicating singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.92,0:33:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像机器一样？\N{\rEnglish}Like a machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.32,0:33:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机器没有智慧，这个有\N{\rEnglish}Machines don't have intelligence. This does.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.64,0:33:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们害怕的人工智能\N{\rEnglish}It's everything we feared about Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.12,0:33:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它早就知道我们要来了\N{\rEnglish}And it knew we were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.10,0:33:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是被太空舱的电子信号引出来\N{\rEnglish}So it was probably drawn out by the electronic signature of the capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.32,0:33:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们自以为了解的宇宙本质都被…\N{\rEnglish}Everything we thought we knew about the nature of the universe has just...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.44,0:33:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彻底推翻了\N{\rEnglish}gone out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.40,0:33:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没准备好\N{\rEnglish}We're not prepared for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.21,0:34:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黛比，不要争论了，快打包行李\N{\rEnglish}Deb, don't argue, just pack your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.75,0:34:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶快逃命\N{\rEnglish}We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.64,0:34:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想落跑？\N{\rEnglish}So you're just gonna quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.84,0:34:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然你要我怎样？\N{\rEnglish}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.15,0:34:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮忙搞清楚那是什么\N{\rEnglish}I want you to help us figure out what the hell this thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.22,0:34:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们好对付它\N{\rEnglish}so we can beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.52,0:34:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有设备\N{\rEnglish}We're not equipped for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.71,0:34:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到我们面对的是什么了\N{\rEnglish}You've seen what we're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.80,0:34:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早就想要我这份工作了，福勒\N{\rEnglish}You've been gunning for my job for a while, Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.40,0:34:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜，送你吧\N{\rEnglish}Congrats, it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.40,0:34:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你隐瞒了什么？\N{\rEnglish}What are you not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.72,0:34:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有Q级别的安全许可权\N{\rEnglish}You've got Q clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.20,0:34:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个洞就在危海\N{\rEnglish}The hole is in the Mare Crisium.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.28,0:34:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈珀公听会上讲的就是那个\N{\rEnglish}That's what the Harper hearings were all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.28,0:34:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想深入NASA的机密\N{\rEnglish}If you're serious about going down the NASA rabbit hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.36,0:34:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就去找霍登菲尔德\N{\rEnglish}you should pay a visit to Holdenfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.72,0:34:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的通行许可证\N{\rEnglish}Here's your clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.37,0:34:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（NASA，阿尔伯特·哈钦斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.13,0:34:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（国家航空航天局 管制区域）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.28,0:35:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么进来的？\N{\rEnglish}How did you get down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.04,0:35:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哈钦斯给我的\N{\rEnglish}Hutchings gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.64,0:35:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要STX-136A所有的资料\N{\rEnglish}I'll need all records of STX-136A.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.16,0:35:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在等什么吗？\N{\rEnglish}You waiting for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.80,0:35:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（布莱恩·哈珀的头盔影像）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.22,0:35:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼？\N{\rEnglish}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.36,0:35:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么…\N{\rEnglish}I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.68,0:35:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛？\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍登菲尔德？\N{\rEnglish}Holdenfield?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.09,0:36:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该动那个\N{\rEnglish}You're not supposed to have that,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.37,0:36:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,136阿尔法\N{\rEnglish}136 Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.60,0:36:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是机密\N{\rEnglish}That's classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.27,0:36:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最高机密\N{\rEnglish}Top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.76,0:36:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NASA为什么要隐瞒这一切？\N{\rEnglish}Why is NASA lying about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.40,0:36:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1969年7月20日\N{\rEnglish}July 20th, 1969.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.36,0:36:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我的一小步”\N{\rEnglish}"One small step for man,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.92,0:36:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“人类的一大步… 废话一大堆”\N{\rEnglish}"one giant leap for..." Yada, yada, yada.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.04,0:36:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在学校学到的是阿波罗11号\N{\rEnglish}In school, you were taught that Apollo 11
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.39,0:36:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和控制中心断了联络\N{\rEnglish}lost contact with Mission Control
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.72,0:36:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长达两分钟\N{\rEnglish}for two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.48,0:36:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是谎言\N{\rEnglish}Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.84,0:36:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制中心切断了他们和世界的连线\N{\rEnglish}Mission Control cut their feed to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.17,0:36:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们那天有个重大发现\N{\rEnglish}because they found something on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.96,0:36:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的搏动闪光\N{\rEnglish}Strange pulsating lights
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.00,0:36:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从月球外壳底下发射出来\N{\rEnglish}emanating from beneath the Moon's crust.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.48,0:36:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被指派隐瞒这件事的人是我\N{\rEnglish}It was me who was assigned to keep it under wraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.60,0:36:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿波罗号人员都配合，大家跟随\N{\rEnglish}The Apollo crew played ball. Everybody after.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.72,0:36:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有布莱恩·哈珀不肯\N{\rEnglish}Just Brian Harper wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.96,0:36:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说他疯了\N{\rEnglish}They called him crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.32,0:36:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像垃圾一样丢了他\N{\rEnglish}Threw him out with the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.84,0:36:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要告诉我的是月球\N{\rEnglish}You're telling me that the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.12,0:37:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是人类史上最大的骗局？\N{\rEnglish}was effectively the biggest cover-up in human history?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.88,0:37:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大？或许吧\N{\rEnglish}Biggest? Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.52,0:37:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的双手也染了血\N{\rEnglish}You had blood on your hands, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.64,0:37:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.76,0:37:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奉命行事的人…\N{\rEnglish}anyone who follows orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.00,0:37:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是共犯吧？\N{\rEnglish}pretty much always does, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.44,0:37:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种科技…\N{\rEnglish}That technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.22,0:37:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领先我们好几百万年\N{\rEnglish}it's light years ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.44,0:37:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相较之下…\N{\rEnglish}Compared to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.21,0:37:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在石器时代\N{\rEnglish}we're the Stone Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.88,0:37:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们阻止它的唯一机会…\N{\rEnglish}The only shot we had to stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.16,0:37:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是ZX-7\N{\rEnglish}was Zulu X-Ray 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.56,0:37:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它被尘封了，束之高阁\N{\rEnglish}It was shut down. Shelved.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.52,0:37:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为预算问题\N{\rEnglish}For budgetary reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.08,0:37:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官，还有更要紧的事等着我…\N{\rEnglish}Well, Commander, I have pressing business waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.17,0:37:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我桌上\N{\rEnglish}on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.88,0:37:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都快要没时间了\N{\rEnglish}The sand in the hourglass is dropping quickly for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.52,0:37:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大势已去了啊\N{\rEnglish}It's as good as gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.96,0:37:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉\N{\rEnglish}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.98,0:37:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\rEnglish}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.80,0:38:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的\N{\rEnglish}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.64,0:38:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\rEnglish}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.48,0:38:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联络不上我儿子\N{\rEnglish}I can't reach my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.20,0:38:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说你以前是个宇航员\N{\rEnglish}Word is, um, you're an astronaut,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.52,0:38:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你一定知道\N{\rEnglish}so you must know that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.71,0:38:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球内部全是农作物\N{\rEnglish}the entire inside of the Moon is full of produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.49,0:38:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，请你告诉这位仁兄\N{\rEnglish}KC, can you tell Birkenstocks here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.12,0:38:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快要想把他扔出窗外了\N{\rEnglish}that I'm dangerously close to hurling him out a window?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.36,0:38:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我们找个空房间\N{\rEnglish}Okay, well, let's find an empty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.92,0:38:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然印加人的马铃薯是哪来的？\N{\rEnglish}How do you think the Incas got their potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.44,0:38:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\rEnglish}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.96,0:38:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过只要我们能毁了这玩意儿…\N{\rEnglish}You said that if we can destroy this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.20,0:38:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们研究过\N{\rEnglish}We have a theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.64,0:38:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球应该会回到原始轨道\N{\rEnglish}that the Moon might return to its original orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.67,0:38:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你提议我们到底要怎么做？\N{\rEnglish}And how do you propose we do that exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.92,0:38:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也说用现代太空船不可行\N{\rEnglish}You said so yourself, using a modern spacecraft is not feasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.40,0:38:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想办法\N{\rEnglish}I am working on a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.20,0:38:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的努力\N{\rEnglish}We appreciate your effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.68,0:38:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在这是军事行动\N{\rEnglish}but this is now a military operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.60,0:38:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来由我们接手\N{\rEnglish}We'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.92,0:39:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格！等等！\N{\rEnglish}Doug! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.84,0:39:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你发射核子武器\N{\rEnglish}If you launch nukes,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.60,0:39:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辐射落尘会害死全世界的人\N{\rEnglish}the global fallout is gonna kill everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.56,0:39:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有谁提到核武了吗？\N{\rEnglish}Who said anything about nukes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是大错特错了\N{\rEnglish}You are making a big mistake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.72,0:39:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你让我先拟定计划\N{\rEnglish}Please, let me put together a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.72,0:39:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有个计划了\N{\rEnglish}We have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.28,0:39:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和吉米跟我一起去科罗拉多吧\N{\rEnglish}Look, why don't you and Jimmy come with me to Colorado?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.00,0:39:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在那儿会很安全\N{\rEnglish}You'll be safe there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.19,0:39:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我做什么？\N{\rEnglish}What are you asking me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.69,0:39:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我放弃吗？\N{\rEnglish}Quit? Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.64,0:39:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是要你为我们的儿子着想\N{\rEnglish}I'm asking you to think about our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.24,0:39:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在为我们的儿子着想\N{\rEnglish}I am thinking about our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.12,0:39:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里？\N{\rEnglish}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.40,0:39:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牢里\N{\rEnglish}Uh, jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好孩子，只是犯了点错\N{\rEnglish}He's a good kid, just made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.92,0:39:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是一直做蠢事\N{\rEnglish}I was always doing stupid things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.80,0:39:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我爸妈怎么受得了我\N{\rEnglish}Don't know how my parents put up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.20,0:39:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们家从来就没什么钱\N{\rEnglish}We never had a lot of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.76,0:39:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有时候我们会买炸鱼薯条\N{\rEnglish}but sometimes we'd all get fish 'n chips,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.24,0:40:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在码头上看星星好几个小时\N{\rEnglish}sit out on the dock and just watch the stars for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.04,0:40:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我第一次梦想当宇航员\N{\rEnglish}That was when I first dreamed of being an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.92,0:40:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我爸过世之后\N{\rEnglish}After my father passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.68,0:40:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈想搬回美国\N{\rEnglish}my mum wanted to move back to the States.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.44,0:40:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说我想当宇航员，我爸还嘲笑我\N{\rEnglish}My dad laughed when I told him I wanted to be an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.92,0:40:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不相信你？\N{\rEnglish}Didn't believe in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.72,0:40:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是委婉的说法\N{\rEnglish}Oh, that's putting it lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.04,0:40:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拼了命才进入NASA\N{\rEnglish}I worked my ass off to get into NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.08,0:40:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看过你上次任务的报导\N{\rEnglish}I read all about your last mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.08,0:40:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到外星人的科技\N{\rEnglish}You saw alien tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.12,0:40:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NASA坚持那是个陨石\N{\rEnglish}And NASA insisted it was a meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.92,0:40:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实不是吗？\N{\rEnglish}But it wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.48,0:40:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过那种东西\N{\rEnglish}It was unlike anything I'd ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.80,0:40:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的是…\N{\rEnglish}And, you know, the worst part
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.56,0:40:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个朋友死在太空中\N{\rEnglish}is I lost a friend up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.04,0:40:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是我的错\N{\rEnglish}And it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.12,0:40:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，怎么会是你的错？\N{\rEnglish}Oh, come on. How was it your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.12,0:40:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你救了太空船、救了福勒\N{\rEnglish}You saved the shuttle. You saved Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.64,0:40:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换来很棒的回报\N{\rEnglish}A lot of good that did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.88,0:40:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离婚、破产，我儿子还恨我\N{\rEnglish}I'm divorced, broke, my son hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.36,0:40:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，我好嫉妒你\N{\rEnglish}God, I am so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.48,0:40:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星人科技\N{\rEnglish}Alien tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.36,0:40:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超赞的\N{\rEnglish}It's freakin' awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.42,0:41:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,极端天气重创东部和墨西哥湾沿岸\N{\rEnglish}Extreme weather is hammering the Eastern Seaboard and Gulf Coast
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.44,0:41:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潮水高涨泛滥造成居民和财产损失\N{\rEnglish}with high tides and flooding wreaking havoc on residents and properties.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.76,0:41:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没前往高处避难的观众\N{\rEnglish}Folks, if you aren't already on high ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.64,0:41:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好尽快赶往高处\N{\rEnglish}you better get there as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.96,0:41:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为一个交换生\N{\rEnglish}Um, as an exchange student,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.28,0:41:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定他们会让我进碉堡吗？\N{\rEnglish}are you sure they're going to let me into the bunker?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.12,0:41:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定，放心吧，我会处理\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. Don't worry about it. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.12,0:41:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.93,0:41:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…以及人口稠密地区的死亡\N{\rEnglish}...and loss of life in populated areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.79,0:41:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从孟加拉传来的画面令人惊心动魄…\N{\rEnglish}As you can see, the images coming out of Bangladesh are simply horrific...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.48,0:41:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会死吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are we gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的，宝贝\N{\rEnglish}No. No, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.00,0:41:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道发生的这一切似乎很可怕\N{\rEnglish}I know all of this that's happening seems so scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.36,0:41:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们不会死，懂吗？\N{\rEnglish}but we are not gonna die. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.64,0:41:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们和爸爸去科罗拉多就安全了\N{\rEnglish}We're all gonna be safe with Dad in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.72,0:41:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还会发射火箭去月球吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you sending more rockets to the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.76,0:41:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.87,0:41:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，你知道为什么吗？因为我们…\N{\rEnglish}No. You know why? Because we don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.84,0:41:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有火箭了\N{\rEnglish}We don't have any more of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.37,0:41:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\rEnglish}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.36,0:41:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为全都在博物馆了\N{\rEnglish}Because they're all in museums.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.60,0:41:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…\N{\rEnglish}And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.20,0:42:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你，宝贝\N{\rEnglish}I love you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.93,0:42:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，道格\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.20,0:42:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZX-7是什么？\N{\rEnglish}What is a ZX-7?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.16,0:42:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁告诉你的？\N{\rEnglish}Who told you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.40,0:42:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，那是什么？\N{\rEnglish}Well, come on. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZX-7是一种电磁脉冲武器\N{\rEnglish}Zulu X-Ray Seven was a prototype EMP device.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.36,0:42:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但研发小组被解散了\N{\rEnglish}But the program got disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.12,0:42:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rEnglish}Okay, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.45,0:42:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显然月球里面那玩意儿是科技产物\N{\rEnglish}it's clear that this thing inside the Moon is technological in nature, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.88,0:42:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他们是认为电磁脉冲武器能解决掉它\N{\rEnglish}I assume they thought an EMP could take the thing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.63,0:42:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法上太空，所以这没有意义\N{\rEnglish}We don't have a way into space so this is a moot point.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.35,0:42:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，测试到什么阶段了？\N{\rEnglish}Okay, well, how far along was the testing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.68,0:42:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔辛达，NASA没核准新任务\N{\rEnglish}Jocinda, NASA isn't cleared for another mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.27,0:42:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就让我来操心吧\N{\rEnglish}How about you let me worry about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.24,0:42:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫星定位系统锁定在着陆区\N{\rEnglish}GPS is locked on L2.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.92,0:42:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,补偿纬度往西负4.5度\N{\rEnglish}Compensate latitude by minus 4.5 west.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.04,0:42:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4.5度，收到\N{\rEnglish}4.5 degrees. Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.32,0:42:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度减为10节\N{\rEnglish}Reducing to 10 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.20,0:43:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门！\N{\rEnglish}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.54,0:43:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪位？ - 布莱恩·哈珀？\N{\rEnglish}- Yeah? - Brian Harper?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.47,0:43:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.19,0:43:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你跟我们走\N{\rEnglish}We need you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事关国家安全\N{\rEnglish}It's a matter of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.21,0:43:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，等我一下\N{\rEnglish}All right. Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.68,0:43:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去哪儿都要带着他\N{\rEnglish}I'm not going anywhere without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.28,0:43:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我们是个团队\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, we're a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.22,0:43:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，小姐\N{\rEnglish}Sorry, I'm sorry, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.44,0:43:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\rEnglish}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.60,0:43:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！\N{\rEnglish}Oh, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.55,0:43:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经将近三小时了\N{\rEnglish}It's been nearly three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.74,0:43:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能是个好兆头\N{\rEnglish}That can't be a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.76,0:43:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃那么多药干嘛？\N{\rEnglish}What's with all the pill popping?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.20,0:43:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你全身冒汗，还好吗？\N{\rEnglish}You're really sweating over there. You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.91,0:43:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.19,0:43:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.91,0:43:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我多次闯入加州大尔湾分校\N{\rEnglish}I broke into UC Irvine multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.64,0:43:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄丢了他们的两支拖把\N{\rEnglish}I lost two of their mops.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.76,0:43:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能知道了\N{\rEnglish}They probably know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.20,0:44:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑？不会吧\N{\rEnglish}Oh, you gotta be kidding me. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.84,0:44:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没比你想在这儿\N{\rEnglish}Look, I don't want to be here any more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.51,0:44:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧\N{\rEnglish}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.34,0:44:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不必再听你的命令了\N{\rEnglish}No, no, no. I don't have to take orders from you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.71,0:44:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好奇，你还在背叛朋友吗？\N{\rEnglish}I'm just curious, you still screwing over your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.60,0:44:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在跟我说话？真的假的？  - 这里有多少人…\N{\rEnglish}- Oh, you talking about me? Really? - How many of these wonderful people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.56,0:44:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了！\N{\rEnglish}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.42,0:44:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是谁？\N{\rEnglish}Who the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.28,0:44:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是KC·豪斯曼博士\N{\rEnglish}Dr. KC Houseman, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.32,0:44:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我写了好几封邮件给你\N{\rEnglish}I wrote you several e-mails,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.21,0:44:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你都没回复\N{\rEnglish}but you never responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.24,0:44:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？\N{\rEnglish}What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.28,0:44:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\rEnglish}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.68,0:44:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们即将看到\N{\rEnglish}What you're about to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.88,0:44:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有极少数人看过的东西\N{\rEnglish}only a handful of people have ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.00,0:44:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC比你们更早知道月球偏离轨道\N{\rEnglish}KC knew the Moon was out of orbit before you guys did.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.96,0:44:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我公开研究结果时社交媒体沸腾了\N{\rEnglish}Social media went wild when I posted my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.12,0:44:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你就是那个不明爆料者？  - 对\N{\rEnglish}- You're the "unidentified source"? - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.68,0:44:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\rEnglish}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.24,0:44:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯利，调阅坑道的画面\N{\rEnglish}Mosley, pull up the tunnel, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.52,0:45:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从指数估计深度超过25公里\N{\rEnglish}Our readings estimate its depth to be over 25 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.44,0:45:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是危海\N{\rEnglish}That's the Mare Crisium.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.71,0:45:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.68,0:45:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想多年前发生的事\N{\rEnglish}I think whatever happened all those years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.96,0:45:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接导致了现在发生的事\N{\rEnglish}is directly responsible for what's happening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.50,0:45:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在相信我了？\N{\rEnglish}So you believe me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.08,0:45:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你的头盔影像\N{\rEnglish}I saw your helmet cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.56,0:45:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在道歉有点迟了\N{\rEnglish}It's a little late for an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.64,0:45:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都被蒙在鼓里\N{\rEnglish}We were both lied to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.40,0:45:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次国际任务不只是出了错\N{\rEnglish}The international mission didn't just go sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.96,0:45:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是遭到攻击了\N{\rEnglish}It was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.13,0:45:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某种高科技生物\N{\rEnglish}A technological life form.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.36,0:45:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧\N{\rEnglish}No effin' way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.80,0:45:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它攻击时，月球试图回到原始的轨道\N{\rEnglish}During the attack, the Moon was attempting to return to its original orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.44,0:45:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到这玩意儿回到月球内部\N{\rEnglish}until this thing went back inside the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.68,0:45:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我一直想告诉你们的事\N{\rEnglish}This is what I've been trying to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.48,0:45:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在入侵这个巨型结构的动力核心\N{\rEnglish}It's doing something to the megastructure's power core.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.93,0:45:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？巨型结构？  - 请你不要问\N{\rEnglish}- Excuse me. The megastructure? - Please don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.32,0:45:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的月球很有可能是外星人造的\N{\rEnglish}It's highly likely our Moon was built by aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.46,0:45:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须进入内部进行第一次接触\N{\rEnglish}We have to get inside and make first contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.85,0:45:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我就叫你不要问了  - 好吧\N{\rEnglish}- I told you not to ask. - All right, look,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.79,0:45:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们计划进行攻击这玩意儿的任务\N{\rEnglish}we're planning a mission to attack this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.08,0:45:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的问题它能感知我们的科技\N{\rEnglish}The only problem is, is it recognizes our technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.76,0:46:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们需要你\N{\rEnglish}Which is why we need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.20,0:46:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我会再听到你说这句话\N{\rEnglish}Well, I never thought I'd hear you say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.56,0:46:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一曾经不用动力就降落太空船的飞行员\N{\rEnglish}You're the only pilot to ever land a shuttle without power.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.44,0:46:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也不是什么特殊技能\N{\rEnglish}Not exactly a hirable skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.48,0:46:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是了\N{\rEnglish}Well, it is right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.14,0:46:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要把你的工作还给你\N{\rEnglish}which is why I'm offering you yourjob back,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.76,0:46:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且…\N{\rEnglish}and...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.97,0:46:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲自…\N{\rEnglish}I'm personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.67,0:46:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恳求你的帮忙\N{\rEnglish}asking you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.24,0:46:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应吧，布莱恩\N{\rEnglish}Say yes, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.92,0:46:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\rEnglish}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.12,0:46:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己有很多问题要解决\N{\rEnglish}I got a lot of my own problems down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.32,0:46:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球要撞上地球…\N{\rEnglish}And the Moon falling onto Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.64,0:46:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是其中之一吗？\N{\rEnglish}isn't one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.92,0:46:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找你来是我错了\N{\rEnglish}I was wrong to bring you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.02,0:46:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说完了\N{\rEnglish}I am done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.24,0:46:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算要怎么上去？\N{\rEnglish}How do you plan on getting up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.12,0:46:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我们的太空船都在博物馆\N{\rEnglish}You know all of our shuttles are in museums.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.96,0:46:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奋进号就在洛杉矶本地\N{\rEnglish}The Endeavour is right here in LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.72,0:46:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且中国要提供月球登陆舱\N{\rEnglish}Plus, the Chinese are offering their prototype moon lander.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.24,0:46:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这听起来很荒谬\N{\rEnglish}I know it sounds completely crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.00,0:46:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你刚才给我们看的东西很荒谬\N{\rEnglish}No, no, what you showed us was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.92,0:46:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在说的远远超越荒谬了\N{\rEnglish}This is a whole other level of insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.96,0:47:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是正适合你吗？\N{\rEnglish}Ought to be right up your alley then, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.04,0:47:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我答应你…\N{\rEnglish}If I do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.72,0:47:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会要求回报\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna need something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.08,0:47:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有找到他吗？\N{\rEnglish}Did you reach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.68,0:47:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，正在处理中\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. It's being handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.60,0:47:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼会到范登堡跟我们碰头\N{\rEnglish}Sonny's gonna meet us at Vandenberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.84,0:47:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们错过派对了\N{\rEnglish}Looks like we missed the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.96,0:47:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至没收到邀请卡\N{\rEnglish}I didn't even get an invite.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.80,0:47:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少有人跟我们同一国了\N{\rEnglish}At least somebody's on the same page as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.85,0:47:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（奋进号，去你的月球）
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.66,0:47:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看我找到什么\N{\rEnglish}Look what I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.04,0:47:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 或许可以当卫生纸用  - 什么？\N{\rEnglish}- Maybe we can use it as toilet paper. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.69,0:47:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的周遭\N{\rEnglish}Take a look around you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.28,0:47:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 钞票没用处了  - 随便啦，走吧\N{\rEnglish}- It's worthless. - Whatever. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.96,0:47:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意：\N{\rEnglish}Attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.24,0:47:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家不要待在街上\N{\rEnglish}we are asking everyone to please clear the streets
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.36,0:47:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在室内…\N{\rEnglish}and to remain indoors...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.20,0:47:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开这里，快！\N{\rEnglish}Dude, dude, we gotta get outta here. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.00,0:48:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，这真是太刺激了，对吧？\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. This is really, really exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.05,0:48:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（新闻快报）
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.72,0:48:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在各国领袖拼命想思考办法时\N{\rEnglish}As leaders around the world struggle for answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.48,0:48:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了新影像显示\N{\rEnglish}new images have surfaced suggesting
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.74,0:48:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NASA可能在计划新的登月任务\N{\rEnglish}that NASA might have plans for a new lunar mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.75,0:48:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但目前为止，NASA和白宫\N{\rEnglish}But so far, NASA and the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.67,0:48:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于问题都不予回应\N{\rEnglish}have not responded to requests for comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.03,0:48:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们东南亚特派员回复的消息\N{\rEnglish}And this is just in from our correspondent in Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.84,0:48:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显然月球造成地壳活动急遽增加\N{\rEnglish}Apparently, the Moon is causing a drastic increase in tectonic activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.68,0:48:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（范登堡空军基地，加州隆波克）\N持续传来无数地震和火山爆发回报\N{\rEnglish}Reports of countless earthquakes and volcanic eruptions keep pouring in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.96,0:48:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪\N{\rEnglish}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.44,0:48:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么奇怪？\N{\rEnglish}What's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.56,0:48:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球的引力不足以导致这种现象\N{\rEnglish}The Moon doesn't have enough gravity to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.24,0:48:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管距离地球多近\N{\rEnglish}no matter how close it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.72,0:48:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还是不懂\N{\rEnglish}You still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.48,0:48:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们面对的是巨型结构\N{\rEnglish}We're dealing with a megastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.88,0:48:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的规则已经不适用了\N{\rEnglish}Your rules don't apply anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.96,0:48:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来了多久？\N{\rEnglish}We've been here how long now,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.79,0:48:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人想上个漆吗？\N{\rEnglish}and nobody's bothered to paint over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.76,0:48:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愈来愈喜欢了\N{\rEnglish}It's kinda growing on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.32,0:49:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼在哪儿？\N{\rEnglish}Hey, where's Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.48,0:49:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我派了地勤人员前往监狱\N{\rEnglish}I sent a ground crew to the prison, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.20,0:49:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我好几天都没听到消息\N{\rEnglish}But I haven't heard anything in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.00,0:49:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不早说？\N{\rEnglish}Why the hell didn't you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.32,0:49:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我需要你专心处理这件事\N{\rEnglish}'Cause I need you to be focused on what's happening right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.76,0:49:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨型结构不用排气系统也能在太空中移动\N{\rEnglish}Megastructures move through space without an exhaust system.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.76,0:49:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球有引擎？\N{\rEnglish}The Moon has an engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.80,0:49:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住这点，我马上回来\N{\rEnglish}Hold that thought. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.48,0:49:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少你老公有遵守约定\N{\rEnglish}Well, at least your husband came through with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.64,0:49:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是前夫\N{\rEnglish}Ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.24,0:49:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 上校  - 福勒局长\N{\rEnglish}- Colonel. - Director Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.64,0:49:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈珀指挥官，我是里德中校\N{\rEnglish}Commander Harper. I'm Lieutenant Colonel Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.72,0:49:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是艾佛利上尉\N{\rEnglish}This is Captain Avery.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.56,0:49:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴维森将军大概告诉我们了\N{\rEnglish}We've been briefed by General Davidson.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.20,0:49:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先带你走一遍装备流程\N{\rEnglish}We need to walk you through the arming procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.60,0:49:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是宇航员，不是军人\N{\rEnglish}I'm an astronaut, not a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.52,0:49:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会带你们到要去的地方\N{\rEnglish}I'll get you where you need to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.80,0:49:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会引爆任何炸弹\N{\rEnglish}but I'm not setting off any bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.16,0:49:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不想要你引爆\N{\rEnglish}We don't expect you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.40,0:49:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会陪你执行任务和启动装置\N{\rEnglish}We'll accompany you on the mission and activate the device,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.28,0:50:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你要熟悉流程，出事时用得上\N{\rEnglish}but you need to be familiar with the process should complications arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹的保全和认证系统都被拆除了\N{\rEnglish}The bomb's security and authentication systems have been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.06,0:50:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是不用地面许可也能安装\N{\rEnglish}Meaning we can arm it without approval from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.52,0:50:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用遥控器引爆\N{\rEnglish}Using a remote trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.56,0:50:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（待命中）\N按两下，再长按这个按钮\N{\rEnglish}Two clicks, then push this down and hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.72,0:50:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能引爆装置了\N{\rEnglish}Triggers the device to go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.44,0:50:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 简单  - 对，简单\N{\rEnglish}- Simple. - Yeah. Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.76,0:50:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到范登堡了，上尉，完毕\N{\rEnglish}Nearing Vandenberg, Captain. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.12,0:50:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\rEnglish}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.92,0:50:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就买个特大份的给你\N{\rEnglish}Should've gotten you the jumbo platter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.12,0:50:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救我出来\N{\rEnglish}Thank you for getting me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.52,0:50:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去谢谢你爸吧\N{\rEnglish}You can thank your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.28,0:50:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划是在月球最靠近地球时升空\N{\rEnglish}Plan is to take off when the Moon is closest to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.24,0:50:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们的目标无法预测\N{\rEnglish}Now, since we're dealing with an unpredictable target,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.56,0:50:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领航就会是关键\N{\rEnglish}navigation is gonna be crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.52,0:50:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的领航员\N{\rEnglish}Our navigator,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.45,0:50:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔·桑德斯会确定我们命中目标\N{\rEnglish}Carl Saunders, is gonna be making sure we hit the mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.27,0:50:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞航工程师汉娜·马丁会即时计算\N{\rEnglish}flight engineer Hannah Martin will run real-time calculations
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.52,0:51:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确保我们能与月球相遇\N{\rEnglish}to ensure that we intercept the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.12,0:51:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们脱离大气层再开始重装燃料\N{\rEnglish}And once we clear the atmosphere, we'll begin the refueling process.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.12,0:51:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好我们SpaceX的朋友\N{\rEnglish}Thankfully our friends at SpaceX
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.36,0:51:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前有个推进燃料库在太空绕行\N{\rEnglish}have a propellant depot currently in orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.00,0:51:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱埃隆\N{\rEnglish}I love Elon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.48,0:51:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到完全关闭电源后\N{\rEnglish}So once we're all powered off,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.36,0:51:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就用推进器对准危海前进\N{\rEnglish}we'll use our thrusters to position ourselves over the Mare Crisium.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.76,0:51:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们中国的朋友临时改造了机上系统\N{\rEnglish}Our Chinese friends have jerry-rigged the onboard systems
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.20,0:51:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让我们能不用电子设备飞行\N{\rEnglish}so that we can fly it without electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.56,0:51:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才能把装了炸弹的登月车停好\N{\rEnglish}So we'll park the rover section of the module with the bomb inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.28,0:51:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后重新启动电子设备\N{\rEnglish}then switch the electronics back on
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.08,0:51:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当成饵来把这玩意儿引诱出洞\N{\rEnglish}and use it as bait to lure this thing out of its hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.08,0:51:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你们再扣扳机…\N{\rEnglish}Then, you guys will pull the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.94,0:51:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了它\N{\rEnglish}and kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.72,0:51:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望这样我们就都能回家了\N{\rEnglish}And then, hopefully, we all can go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.84,0:51:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果还有家可回的话\N{\rEnglish}If we still have one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.12,0:51:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说错了什么？\N{\rEnglish}What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.36,0:51:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼\N{\rEnglish}Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.61,0:51:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，儿子，还好你没事\N{\rEnglish}Oh, my God, son. Thank God you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.23,0:51:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.24,0:51:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 等等  - 好\N{\rEnglish}- Hold on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.64,0:51:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先确认一下\N{\rEnglish}Just so I'm clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.95,0:52:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要带着炸弹上太空\N{\rEnglish}you're gonna take a bomb into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.11,0:52:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来这儿干嘛？你痛恨NASA\N{\rEnglish}And why are you even here? You hate NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.99,0:52:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你试着理解\N{\rEnglish}Just try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.29,0:52:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一点点机率这计划行得通…\N{\rEnglish}If there's even the smallest chance that this could work...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.00,0:52:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 万一失败呢？  - 只许成功\N{\rEnglish}- What if it doesn't? - It has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.52,0:52:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想给你一个可以平安长大的世界\N{\rEnglish}I want you to have a world you can grow up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.24,0:52:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你成为比我更好的人\N{\rEnglish}Where you can be a better man than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.44,0:52:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去那儿看到了什么？\N{\rEnglish}What have you seen since you've been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.40,0:52:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就太空船那些啊\N{\rEnglish}The space shuttle and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.56,0:52:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想我吗？\N{\rEnglish}Do you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.16,0:52:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我超想你的\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, I really miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.20,0:52:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想你，小家伙\N{\rEnglish}I miss you, too, my little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.44,0:52:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在吗？\N{\rEnglish}Is Mom around?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.96,0:52:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈，爸爸找你\N{\rEnglish}Mom, it's Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.99,0:52:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福勒长官
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.24,0:52:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们去练习零重力加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.99,0:52:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，好的，我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.32,0:52:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他中文有进步了\N{\rEnglish}He's getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.40,0:52:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？\N{\rEnglish}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.80,0:52:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我履行了我的承诺\N{\rEnglish}I held up my end of the bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.72,0:52:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你和吉米到科罗拉多\N{\rEnglish}I want you and Jimmy in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.64,0:52:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会去\N{\rEnglish}We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.34,0:52:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等太空船一升空我们就搭机离开\N{\rEnglish}We're gonna be airlifted out of here as soon as the shuttle launches.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.96,0:53:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被人知道我为你做了什么…\N{\rEnglish}Look, if anyone finds out what I've done for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.68,0:53:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的\N{\rEnglish}They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.64,0:53:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要确定…\N{\rEnglish}You just make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.26,0:53:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那些嗜杀同袍不要碰核武就好了\N{\rEnglish}your trigger-happy buddies keep their hands off the nukes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.20,0:53:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，两位\N{\rEnglish}Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.96,0:53:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有低脂牛奶了，到处都找不到\N{\rEnglish}Out of 2%. I looked everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.04,0:53:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，这样就可以了，谢谢\N{\rEnglish}Nah, this is great. Thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.52,0:53:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差点就进NASA工作了\N{\rEnglish}You know, I almost got a job at NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.00,0:53:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个部门？\N{\rEnglish}What department?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.72,0:53:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清洁管理\N{\rEnglish}Janitorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.64,0:53:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出去！\N{\rEnglish}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.84,0:53:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑住！\N{\rEnglish}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.76,0:53:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们目前估算的月球轨道吗？\N{\rEnglish}Is this your current projected lunar orbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.16,0:53:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对  - 怎么了？\N{\rEnglish}- Yeah. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.56,0:53:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显然没把月球质量增加算进去\N{\rEnglish}This obviously isn't accounting for the Moon's increased mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.72,0:54:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看轨道偏移后的地震活动\N{\rEnglish}Look at all this seismic activity in the wake of its orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.71,0:54:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都知道月球的表面重力\N{\rEnglish}We know the Moon's surface gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.45,0:54:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是1.62米每平方秒\N{\rEnglish}is 1.62 meters squared.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.88,0:54:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少以前是这样\N{\rEnglish}At least it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.20,0:54:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是错的\N{\rEnglish}So this must be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.80,0:54:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，福勒局长，出问题了\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry, Director Fowler, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.20,0:54:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是我们需要的，该死的地震\N{\rEnglish}Just what we need, a damn earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.00,0:54:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷却剂流失了\N{\rEnglish}We're losing coolant.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.48,0:54:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有办法可以修理\N{\rEnglish}Well, there has to be a way to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.08,0:54:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里不行，我们需要在米丘德的整个团队\N{\rEnglish}Not here. We would need the entire team at Michoud
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.32,0:54:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能修复这样的东西\N{\rEnglish}to rebuild something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.64,0:54:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就打电话找人来帮忙啊\N{\rEnglish}Well, then get on the horn and find somebody who can help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.24,0:54:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以帮忙的人都在这儿了\N{\rEnglish}Anyone that can help us is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.52,0:54:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着…\N{\rEnglish}Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.73,0:54:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须考虑\N{\rEnglish}we have to think about
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.52,0:54:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这些人送到安全的地方\N{\rEnglish}letting all of these people here get to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.00,0:54:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全的地方？\N{\rEnglish}To safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.52,0:54:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人连地球都要没了\N{\rEnglish}These people here won't have a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.58,0:54:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非我们解决这个问题\N{\rEnglish}unless we figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.44,0:54:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，我们损失了一具引擎\N{\rEnglish}Brian, we're down an engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.40,0:54:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不可能发射升空了\N{\rEnglish}Launching is no longer an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.16,0:55:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你把我找来\N{\rEnglish}Thanks for bringing me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.36,0:55:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家听我说\N{\rEnglish}May I have everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.44,0:55:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们做的已经超出了我们的要求\N{\rEnglish}You've all done more than we ever could have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.88,0:55:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请接受我最深的谢意\N{\rEnglish}You have my deepest thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.80,0:55:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全国人民都感谢你们\N{\rEnglish}along with the thanks of the entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.04,0:55:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们现在该回家了\N{\rEnglish}But it's now time for you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.80,0:55:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下令所有人员即刻撤离范登堡\N{\rEnglish}I'm ordering the immediate evacuation of all personnel from Vandenberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.04,0:55:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到科罗拉多和家人会合\N{\rEnglish}You'll meet up with your families in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.08,0:55:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸？\N{\rEnglish}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.32,0:55:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾没能成功\N{\rEnglish}I'm sorry it didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我习惯了啦\N{\rEnglish}Story of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.96,0:55:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救我出狱\N{\rEnglish}Thanks for getting me out of jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.80,0:55:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去收拾东西吧，该走了\N{\rEnglish}Let's get our stuff. It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.28,0:55:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间到\N{\rEnglish}Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.48,0:56:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直升机准备好了，我们走吧\N{\rEnglish}Chopper's ready. Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.44,0:56:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先去，我随后就到\N{\rEnglish}Go ahead. I'll meet you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.92,0:56:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么还在这儿？\N{\rEnglish}Why are you guys still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.24,0:56:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福勒局长\N{\rEnglish}Director Fowler,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.82,0:56:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等月球转回来时\N{\rEnglish}when it comes back around,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.76,0:56:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球引力会超过地球拉力的80%\N{\rEnglish}the Moon's gravity will be over 80% of the Earth's pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.36,0:56:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道听起来很扯，但我们检查过豪斯曼博士的数据\N{\rEnglish}I know how it sounds, but we checked Dr. Houseman's data.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.00,0:56:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数字是正确的\N{\rEnglish}The numbers are solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.16,0:56:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给局长看看我们的新模拟\N{\rEnglish}Show the director our new simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.08,0:56:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射时限必须提早\N{\rEnglish}We have to pull up our launch window.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.66,0:56:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才没在听吗？\N{\rEnglish}Guys, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.09,0:56:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己看\N{\rEnglish}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.84,0:56:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有发射时限\N{\rEnglish}There is no launch window.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.12,0:56:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务结束了\N{\rEnglish}The mission's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.24,0:56:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，等一下\N{\rEnglish}Wait. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.76,0:56:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能驾驶只有两具引擎的太空船吗？\N{\rEnglish}How do you feel about flying the shuttle with only two engines?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.80,0:56:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\rEnglish}It can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.15,0:57:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果月球在我们正上方时发射升空\N{\rEnglish}If we launch when the Moon is directly above us,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.08,0:57:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增强的引力应该能推进太空船\N{\rEnglish}the increased gravitational pull should give the shuttle a boost,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.96,0:57:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常有机会让你进入轨道\N{\rEnglish}giving you a really good chance of getting into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.88,0:57:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疏散了我的整个飞航小组\N{\rEnglish}You evacuated my entire flight crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.04,0:57:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法单独操控太空船\N{\rEnglish}I can't fly the shuttle alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.20,0:57:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要跟你去\N{\rEnglish}That's why I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.24,0:57:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人会留下来指挥发射升空\N{\rEnglish}My guys will stay back and handle the launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.88,0:57:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的时间非常有限\N{\rEnglish}But we've got a very narrow window of time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.20,0:57:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你28分钟内要准备好\N{\rEnglish}You'd have to be ready to go in exactly 28 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.04,0:57:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你驾驶，我导航\N{\rEnglish}You fly and I'll navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.32,0:57:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像以前一样\N{\rEnglish}Just like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.68,0:57:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？\N{\rEnglish}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.48,0:57:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个电磁脉冲武器呢？\N{\rEnglish}What about the EMP device?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.89,0:57:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在登月舱上面\N{\rEnglish}It's still in the Moon Lander.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.26,0:57:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少了团队，我们要自行引爆，可是…\N{\rEnglish}I mean, we lost the crew so we're gonna have to set it off ourselves, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.52,0:57:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有注意听吧？\N{\rEnglish}you paid attention, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.20,0:57:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按两下，再长按这个按钮\N{\rEnglish}Two clicks, then press the button down and hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.32,0:57:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能引爆装置了\N{\rEnglish}Triggers the device to go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.37,0:57:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简单\N{\rEnglish}Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.20,0:57:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是你想出来的？\N{\rEnglish}You figured all this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.36,0:57:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还计算出新的发射轨道\N{\rEnglish}And he calculated our new launch trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.32,0:57:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少了电子设备\N{\rEnglish}You know, without electronics,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.08,0:57:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在太空中需要快速计算\N{\rEnglish}we're gonna need to make split-second calculations up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.00,0:57:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们没了飞行工程师\N{\rEnglish}Plus, we lost our flight engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.40,0:57:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.43,0:57:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦\N{\rEnglish}No, no, no, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.64,0:58:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没取得许可\N{\rEnglish}I'm not cleared for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.92,0:58:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是NASA的现任局长\N{\rEnglish}Well, I'm the acting director of NASA,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.36,0:58:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才许可你了，恭喜\N{\rEnglish}so Ijust cleared you. Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.84,0:58:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啦，可是…\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.44,0:58:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有IBS\N{\rEnglish}I've got IBS.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.04,0:58:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大肠激躁症\N{\rEnglish}Irritable Bowel Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.86,0:58:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有动晕症\N{\rEnglish}I get motion sickness, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.52,0:58:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你一直梦想成为宇航员\N{\rEnglish}You said you always wanted to be an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.48,0:58:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有损害性焦虑…\N{\rEnglish}I have debilitating anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.08,0:58:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，如果月球真的是你想的那样\N{\rEnglish}KC, if the Moon really is what you think it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.04,0:58:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会需要一位巨型结构学家\N{\rEnglish}we're gonna need a megastructurist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.24,0:58:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,着装吧\N{\rEnglish}Suit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.04,0:58:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加快，快点！快点！\N{\rEnglish}Expedite. Let's move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.64,0:58:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我输入了你爸的电话号码\N{\rEnglish}So, I've put your dad's number in here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.64,0:58:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道你会去\N{\rEnglish}He knows you're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.84,0:58:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我有时很难搞\N{\rEnglish}I know I wasn't always easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.85,0:58:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样啦\N{\rEnglish}That makes two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.52,0:58:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这是你的主意，对吧？\N{\rEnglish}You know this was all your idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.16,0:58:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很聪明\N{\rEnglish}You're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.28,0:59:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我要你勇敢\N{\rEnglish}But now, I need you to be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.32,0:59:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要你去\N{\rEnglish}I don't want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.92,0:59:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你多过天上所有的星星\N{\rEnglish}I love you more than all the stars in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.12,0:59:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比整条银河还要多吗？\N{\rEnglish}Even more than the whole Milky Way?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.16,0:59:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多很多\N{\rEnglish}Way more.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.48,0:59:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多很多\N{\rEnglish}Way more.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.52,0:59:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好照顾他\N{\rEnglish}Take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.48,0:59:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要注意安全\N{\rEnglish}Be safe up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.68,0:59:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去，希望你用不上\N{\rEnglish}Take this. I hope you don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.44,0:59:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要走主要道路\N{\rEnglish}Stay off the main roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.76,0:59:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸，我…  - 去吧\N{\rEnglish}- Dad, I... - Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.40,0:59:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会发动车子吧？\N{\rEnglish}You do know how to start a car, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.44,0:59:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须警告你\N{\rEnglish}I should warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.01,0:59:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的驾照被吊销了\N{\rEnglish}My license has been revoked.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.24,1:00:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要马上准备\N{\rEnglish}We need to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.84,1:00:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈，你绝对不会相信我要去哪儿\N{\rEnglish}Mum, you're never gonna believe where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.28,1:00:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克，你几时要回家吃晚饭？\N{\rEnglish}Jack, when are you coming home for supper?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.20,1:00:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈，我是KC，你儿子\N{\rEnglish}Mum, this is KC. Your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.40,1:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我逼他们听，他们听了\N{\rEnglish}You told me to make them listen, and they did.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.00,1:00:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些太空装是哪来的？二手店？\N{\rEnglish}Where'd you get these suits from? A thrift shop?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.24,1:00:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早期的阿波罗号\N{\rEnglish}Early Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.66,1:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有电子设备，应该没问题\N{\rEnglish}No electronics, we should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.68,1:00:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该？真是振奋人心啊\N{\rEnglish}"Should be"? That's encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.62,1:00:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出动了\N{\rEnglish}Let's go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.32,1:00:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豪斯曼太太，我们要走了\N{\rEnglish}Mrs. Houseman, we need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.76,1:00:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈？\N{\rEnglish}Mum?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.46,1:00:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我跟护士说话\N{\rEnglish}Let me speak to the nurse.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.52,1:00:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂？  - 你们要撤离了吗？\N{\rEnglish}- HeHo? - Are you evacuating?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.37,1:00:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时出发\N{\rEnglish}Any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.80,1:00:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你照顾好我妈\N{\rEnglish}Please take care of my mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.24,1:00:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\rEnglish}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.76,1:00:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生，我们动作要快\N{\rEnglish}Sir, we have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.76,1:01:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要绑得很紧，懂吗？\N{\rEnglish}This is gonna be really tight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.92,1:01:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开辅助动力一、二和三号\N{\rEnglish}Turn on APU one, two and three.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.20,1:01:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辅助动力启动\N{\rEnglish}APUs active.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.36,1:01:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喷气操纵系统，启动\N{\rEnglish}Reaction Control System, active.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.84,1:01:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自动驾驶，启动\N{\rEnglish}Autopilot active.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.71,1:01:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒数三十秒\N{\rEnglish}T-minus 30.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.28,1:01:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奋进号，有个巨大重力波在靠近你们\N{\rEnglish}Endeavour, you have got a big-ass gravity wave coming your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.48,1:01:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们必须马上升空，完毕\N{\rEnglish}You have to launch now. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.40,1:01:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是说“重力波”吗？\N{\rEnglish}Did he say "gravity wave"?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.68,1:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们赶快走\N{\rEnglish}Guys, get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.00,1:01:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒数十\N{\rEnglish}T-minus ten,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.39,1:01:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九\N{\rEnglish}nine,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.52,1:01:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八\N{\rEnglish}eight,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.48,1:01:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 七…  - 管它的，直接点火\N{\rEnglish}- seven... - Screw it, go for ignition.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.14,1:02:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快上来\N{\rEnglish}Get up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.26,1:02:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Got you!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.80,1:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会很惊险！\N{\rEnglish}This is gonna be close.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.84,1:02:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要被淹没了\N{\rEnglish}We're underwater, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.36,1:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回车上！\N{\rEnglish}Get back in the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.82,1:03:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（警告：上升轨道）
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.92,1:03:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的上升轨道偏移了\N{\rEnglish}Our ascent trajectory is off.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.72,1:03:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右侧推进器失去推进力\N{\rEnglish}The right booster's losing thrust.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.86,1:03:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（警告）
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.72,1:03:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推进力降到0\N{\rEnglish}Thruster's down to zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.20,1:04:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在往右漂移\N{\rEnglish}We're drifting right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.50,1:04:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前是11度\N{\rEnglish}We're at 11 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.20,1:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12度\N{\rEnglish}Twelve.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.38,1:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13度\N{\rEnglish}Thirteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.28,1:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好赶快想办法，否则会坠毁\N{\rEnglish}We better do something fast or we're gonna crash down!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.91,1:04:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道我就不该来啦\N{\rEnglish}I knew I should never have come!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.33,1:04:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关掉另一侧推进器，看看月球能否拉着我们前进\N{\rEnglish}Let's lose the other booster and see if the Moon can pull us the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.25,1:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，可以吗？\N{\rEnglish}KC, can we do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.73,1:04:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快说啊\N{\rEnglish}Come on, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.65,1:04:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前的动量…引力…\N{\rEnglish}Current momentum... Gravity...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.52,1:04:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可以吗？  - 我不知道啦\N{\rEnglish}- Can we do it? - Oh, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.24,1:04:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分离固体火箭助推器\N{\rEnglish}Go for SRB separation.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.64,1:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成\N{\rEnglish}Completed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.04,1:04:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，失败的话我们就死定了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, God, if this doesn't work, we're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.28,1:04:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，最好成功啦\N{\rEnglish}Well, yeah, this better work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.00,1:04:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主燃料箱空了\N{\rEnglish}Main tank's down to zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.32,1:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 乔，扔了它  - 分离主燃料箱\N{\rEnglish}- Jo, get rid of it. - Separating main tank.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.02,1:04:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（第二阶段开始，主燃料箱分离）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.68,1:04:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，我们速度太慢了\N{\rEnglish}Bri, we're going too slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.64,1:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（脱离速度底限）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.60,1:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们完蛋了啦\N{\rEnglish}We're not gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.48,1:05:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\rEnglish}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.63,1:05:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看我们的速度\N{\rEnglish}Look at our velocity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.84,1:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在持续上升\N{\rEnglish}It's still going up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.77,1:05:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位？\N{\rEnglish}Guys...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.40,1:05:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们KSOQ电台即将最后播送\N{\rEnglish}Well, we're about to end our final broadcast here on radio KSOQ.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.16,1:05:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也该逃离去了\N{\rEnglish}Time to seek shelter,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.66,1:06:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱你们心爱的人，享受最后时刻\N{\rEnglish}hug your loved ones, and make these last moments count.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.68,1:06:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循环播放几首老歌希望能一扫阴霾\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna put some oldies on a loop to lighten up your mood.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.44,1:06:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？\N{\rEnglish}What do those mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.60,1:06:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我爸妈的名字\N{\rEnglish}It's my parents' names.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.48,1:06:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有个类似的\N{\rEnglish}I've got one kinda like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.43,1:06:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔纳斯兄弟？\N{\rEnglish}"Jonas Brothers"?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.16,1:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rEnglish}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.10,1:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑啦，真是的\N{\rEnglish}Just messing with you. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.28,1:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情真好笑\N{\rEnglish}Your face was priceless.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.36,1:06:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，不要这样吓我\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.40,1:06:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟，该打电话给你爸了\N{\rEnglish}Hey, buddy, now's probably a good time to call your dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.88,1:06:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸？  - 嗨，你们还好吗？\N{\rEnglish}- Dad? - Hey, are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.96,1:06:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好\N{\rEnglish}Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.72,1:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼开车很快，躲过了那些洪水\N{\rEnglish}Sonny drove fast away from all the crazy water.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.88,1:07:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开车？\N{\rEnglish}Drove?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.02,1:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼是谁？\N{\rEnglish}Who's Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.76,1:07:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢？\N{\rEnglish}Where's Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.68,1:07:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她留下来帮忙了\N{\rEnglish}She stayed behind to help.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.40,1:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，我是布莱恩·哈珀的儿子\N{\rEnglish}Hi, sir, this is Brian Harper's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.44,1:07:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要去找你\N{\rEnglish}We're on our way to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.88,1:07:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要再几百哩，但我们开得很快\N{\rEnglish}We still have a few hundred miles to go, but we 're making good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.88,1:07:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的守卫很森严\N{\rEnglish}Security's extremely tight here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.24,1:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快到了告诉我，我会下令放行\N{\rEnglish}Call when you get close so I can get you clearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.32,1:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，谢谢你\N{\rEnglish}Will do. Thank you so much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.24,1:07:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，谢谢你照顾我儿子\N{\rEnglish}No, thank you for looking after my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.76,1:07:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，KC\N{\rEnglish}Okay, KC,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.67,1:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我教你的那样慢慢动作\N{\rEnglish}very gently with the maneuver just like Ishowed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.76,1:07:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.85,1:07:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来\N{\rEnglish}Very gently.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.90,1:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEnglish}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.06,1:07:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以\N{\rEnglish}I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.13,1:07:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（奋进号）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.05,1:07:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点\N{\rEnglish}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.76,1:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在切换成定位维持模式\N{\rEnglish}Now switch to station-keeping mode,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.81,1:07:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来由我们接手\N{\rEnglish}and we 'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.37,1:07:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才做的事我自己也不敢相信\N{\rEnglish}I can't believe I just did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.23,1:07:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定你以前没做过吗？\N{\rEnglish}You sure you've never done this before?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.64,1:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我十岁那年在万圣节扮成宇航员\N{\rEnglish}When I was 10, I dressed up as an astronaut for Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.76,1:07:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特·艾波索说我上不了太空，因为我太胖了\N{\rEnglish}Scottie Ebersol told me I 'd never go to space 'cause I was too chubby.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.48,1:08:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望斯科特现在能看见你\N{\rEnglish}If only Scottie Ebersol could see you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.12,1:08:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，KC，打开太空燃料箱上面的加油阀\N{\rEnglish}Okay, KC, open the fueling valves on the shuttle tank.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.20,1:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是写着加油阀的那些小开关\N{\rEnglish}It's those little switches that say fueling valves.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.52,1:08:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到，加油阀都打开了\N{\rEnglish}Roger. Fueling valves wide open.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.20,1:08:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\rEnglish}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.12,1:08:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要告解一件事\N{\rEnglish}Ihave a confession to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.16,1:08:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我事先不知道 你会不会答应这次任务\N{\rEnglish}I didn't know if you'd be able to follow through with any of this, Bri.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.84,1:08:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要告解一件事\N{\rEnglish}You know, I have a confession to make, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.76,1:08:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是“我祈愿非洲下雨”\N{\rEnglish}It is "I bless the rains down in Africa. "
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.00,1:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我查了歌词\N{\rEnglish}I looked it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.68,1:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就说嘛\N{\rEnglish}Itold you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.00,1:08:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，请你关闭加油阀\N{\rEnglish}KC, close the fueling valves, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.28,1:08:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（太空船燃料箱全满）
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.76,1:08:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油阀已经关闭\N{\rEnglish}Fueling valves are closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.40,1:08:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔，转过去看看\N{\rEnglish}Jo, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.67,1:08:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要赶快走了\N{\rEnglish}We need to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.25,1:08:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望不会太迟\N{\rEnglish}And I hope it's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.06,1:08:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.24,1:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着月球轨道愈来愈靠近地表\N{\rEnglish}As the Moon's orbit brings it closer to the surface,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.28,1:09:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科学家警告会有极端的重力效应\N{\rEnglish}scientists have warned of extreme gravitational effects.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.08,1:09:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚糟透了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, what a night.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.92,1:09:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我车子抛锚，可以搭个便车吗？\N{\rEnglish}Hey, my car crapped out on me. Do you think you could give me a lift?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.92,1:09:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下车！\N{\rEnglish}Out!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.56,1:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上\N{\rEnglish}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.00,1:09:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我讲第二遍\N{\rEnglish}Don't make me ask twice!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.56,1:09:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点\N{\rEnglish}Be cool. Be cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.40,1:09:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！放了她！\N{\rEnglish}Stop! Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.16,1:09:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，转过去\N{\rEnglish}All right. Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.40,1:09:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背包里装了什么？\N{\rEnglish}What's in the bag, kid?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.30,1:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照他说的做
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.55,1:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.93,1:09:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再讲外星话了\N{\rEnglish}Enough of that gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.89,1:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别伤害他  - 闭嘴！\N{\rEnglish}- Hey, don't hurt him. - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.35,1:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，大家都冷静！\N{\rEnglish}All right, everyone calm down!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.20,1:09:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是自以为是啊\N{\rEnglish}Look at Mr. Smartass.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.08,1:09:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个大学生吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are you a college boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.86,1:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，走吧\N{\rEnglish}All right. Let's roll.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.12,1:10:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.04,1:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手机还在吉米的背包里\N{\rEnglish}The phone is still in Jimmy's backpack.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.08,1:10:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要怎么进碉堡？\N{\rEnglish}How are we gonna get into the bunker?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.36,1:10:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要另一辆车，但我知道哪里有\N{\rEnglish}We're gonna need another car but I think I know where to get one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.72,1:10:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.88,1:10:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关闭通用电脑\N{\rEnglish}Shutting off general-purpose computers.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.12,1:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,截断主电力母线\N{\rEnglish}Go ahead and kill the main power busses.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.16,1:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\rEnglish}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.24,1:10:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果休斯顿中心还在\N{\rEnglish}Well, if there was still a Houston,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.72,1:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在应该要抓狂了\N{\rEnglish}they'd be freaking out about now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.56,1:10:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几百年前的疯狂水手用那个老东西在海上导航\N{\rEnglish}Crazy sailors used that old thing centuries ago to navigate the seas.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.36,1:10:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她保持专注，否则我们会跑去海王星\N{\rEnglish}Let her concentrate or we're gonna end up on Neptune.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.04,1:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KC，给我93分钟后月球的位置\N{\rEnglish}KC, give me the position of the Moon in 93 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.36,1:10:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.93,1:10:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假设月球目前的位置\N{\rEnglish}Assuming the Moon's current position,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.12,1:10:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…\N{\rEnglish}then it will be at, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.53,1:10:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纬度3度，往南12分\N{\rEnglish}Latitude three degrees,12 minutes south.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.32,1:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纬度5度，往西12分\N{\rEnglish}Longitude five degrees, 12 minutes west.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.00,1:11:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，开始43秒的喷射吧\N{\rEnglish}Bri, let's start with a 43-second burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.36,1:11:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解\N{\rEnglish}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.68,1:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三、二、一\N{\rEnglish}Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.88,1:11:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看\N{\rEnglish}Hey, guys. Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.00,1:11:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续走\N{\rEnglish}Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.21,1:11:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.40,1:11:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望月球能撑得住\N{\rEnglish}I hope the Moon holds together.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.97,1:11:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少再撑一会儿\N{\rEnglish}At least for a little while, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.76,1:11:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把太空船掉头\N{\rEnglish}Turning us around.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.60,1:12:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.74,1:12:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轨道操作系统喷射八到十秒\N{\rEnglish}Stay between eight to 10 seconds on the OMS burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.07,1:12:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\rEnglish}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.00,1:12:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要踩煞车了\N{\rEnglish}Hitting the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.28,1:12:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音不太妙\N{\rEnglish}Oh, that doesn't sound too good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.60,1:12:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事啦\N{\rEnglish}She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.76,1:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们不需要那个\N{\rEnglish}Hope we don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.76,1:12:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米，牵着我的手\N{\rEnglish}Jimmy, hold my hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.12,1:12:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快走！快点！\N{\rEnglish}Come on. Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.84,1:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米！抓紧！\N{\rEnglish}Jimmy! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.60,1:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放手！\N{\rEnglish}Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.63,1:13:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔！\N{\rEnglish}Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.48,1:13:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了\N{\rEnglish}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.24,1:13:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开飞行模式了\N{\rEnglish}It's on airplane mode.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.36,1:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备登月舱\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna get the lander ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.84,1:13:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.92,1:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去给他们好看，指挥官\N{\rEnglish}Go get 'em, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.44,1:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登月车电子设备启动\N{\rEnglish}Rover electronics activated.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.40,1:15:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,返回奋进号\N{\rEnglish}Returning to the Endeavour.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.92,1:15:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法想像回到太空对他有多难\N{\rEnglish}I can't imagine how hard it is for him to be back up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.16,1:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这里才是他的归属之地\N{\rEnglish}Up here is where he belongs, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.60,1:15:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还在为你们上次任务的事而自责\N{\rEnglish}He still blames himself for what happened on your last mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.20,1:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他觉得是他害死了那个宇航员\N{\rEnglish}Thinks that astronaut dying was his fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.92,1:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该走了\N{\rEnglish}We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.56,1:15:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.72,1:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何毫无动静？\N{\rEnglish}Why is nothing happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.92,1:15:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（待机中）
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.46,1:15:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（启动）
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.60,1:15:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…\N{\rEnglish}Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.28,1:16:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它上钩了\N{\rEnglish}It's taking the bait.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.52,1:16:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快啊，快啊，快啊\N{\rEnglish}Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.12,1:16:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它在等什么？  - 不太对劲\N{\rEnglish}- What's it waiting for? - Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.20,1:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们必须爆了它  - 但它太远了\N{\rEnglish}- We have to take it out. - No, it's too far away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.96,1:16:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行不通\N{\rEnglish}It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.79,1:16:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往我们这边过来了\N{\rEnglish}It's headed our way.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.20,1:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩…\N{\rEnglish}Bri...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.44,1:16:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它不停啊！ - 我看得出来\N{\rEnglish}- It's not stopping! - I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.76,1:17:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手机！KC，你的手机，关掉！\N{\rEnglish}Your phone. KC, your phone. Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.24,1:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点…\N{\rEnglish}Come on! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.92,1:17:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该早点关机的\N{\rEnglish}Could've just turned it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.60,1:17:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，布莱恩\N{\rEnglish}Okay, Bri,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.75,1:17:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在审讯时，你说过当“巨群”回过头来\N{\rEnglish}at the trial, you said when the swarm came back,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.88,1:17:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它未攻击奋进号，对吧？\N{\rEnglish}it didn't attack the Endeavour, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.90,1:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.68,1:17:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电子设备故障了\N{\rEnglish}The electronics were out.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.64,1:17:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以它当时才没攻击我们\N{\rEnglish}That's why it didn't attack us then,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.00,1:17:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为这样刚才没被炸弹引过去\N{\rEnglish}and that's why it didn't go after the bomb just now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.12,1:18:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它要两者都侦测到\N{\rEnglish}Because it needs to sense both.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.96,1:18:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛程序是设计成要它找出电子设备中的生物\N{\rEnglish}It's like it's programmed to seek out organic matter in an electronic environment.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.63,1:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对  - 基本上就是我们\N{\rEnglish}- Exactly. - And that's basically us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.36,1:18:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是人类\N{\rEnglish}That's humans.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.84,1:18:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位，还有另一个问题\N{\rEnglish}And guys, we have another problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.83,1:18:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军方\N{\rEnglish}The military.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.95,1:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们准备用尽现有的一切阻止月球\N{\rEnglish}They're prepared to use everything at their disposal to stop the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.55,1:18:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是认真的吧\N{\rEnglish}You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.68,1:18:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常认真\N{\rEnglish}I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.68,1:18:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要用核武攻击\N{\rEnglish}They're gonna nuke it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.82,1:18:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那辐射尘呢？\N{\rEnglish}What about the radioactive fallout?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.40,1:18:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友有提到吗？\N{\rEnglish}Your buddies say anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.73,1:18:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先，他们不是我的朋友\N{\rEnglish}Well, first of all, they're not my buddies.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.43,1:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没想着明天，只想着活过今天\N{\rEnglish}And they're not thinking about tomorrow. They're trying to survive today.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.20,1:18:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是他们的大计划？\N{\rEnglish}So that's their grand plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.92,1:18:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大老远来这里不能失败\N{\rEnglish}I didn't come this far to fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.56,1:18:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要想个办法宰了它\N{\rEnglish}We have to figure out a way to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.76,1:18:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要驾驶登月舱去追杀它\N{\rEnglish}I'm taking the lander and flying after this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.36,1:18:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他意思是要进入月球内部？\N{\rEnglish}Does he mean inside the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.64,1:18:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，恐怕他正是这个意思\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, I'm afraid that's exactly what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.88,1:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还要多久才会发射？\N{\rEnglish}How much time left till they launch?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.44,1:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，他们没告诉我\N{\rEnglish}I don't know. They didn't exactly tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.04,1:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果他们打算用洲际导弹\N{\rEnglish}But if they plan on using ICBMs, then they're gonna
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.08,1:18:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得等到月亮进入平流层才行\N{\rEnglish}have to wait until the Moon enters the stratosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.32,1:18:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下不到两小时了\N{\rEnglish}That's less than two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.24,1:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是私人土地\N{\rEnglish}This is private property.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.07,1:19:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头吧\N{\rEnglish}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.40,1:19:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈住这儿\N{\rEnglish}My mom lives here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.36,1:19:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是布兰达罗培兹的儿子\N{\rEnglish}I'm Brenda Lopez's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.76,1:19:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没看过那个小子\N{\rEnglish}I've never seen that kid before.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.66,1:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去呼叫23号\N{\rEnglish}Radio unit 23.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.35,1:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在这儿\N{\rEnglish}Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.48,1:19:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我只是想进去我家\N{\rEnglish}Okay, I just need to get to my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.52,1:19:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要开车\N{\rEnglish}To get the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.83,1:19:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 拜托你们  - 待在原地别动\N{\rEnglish}- Please. - Stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.73,1:19:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则我会再开枪\N{\rEnglish}Or I'll shoot again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.16,1:19:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有权捍卫我的土地，汤姆\N{\rEnglish}I have a right to defend my property, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.04,1:19:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯伦，够了！\N{\rEnglish}Karen, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.96,1:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴你没事\N{\rEnglish}Hey, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.28,1:19:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来像没事吗？\N{\rEnglish}Do I look okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.30,1:19:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你突然跑到山上？\N{\rEnglish}You took off to the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.91,1:19:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有法庭都关闭了\N{\rEnglish}All the courts were closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.93,1:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我日夜都在打电话想办法救你\N{\rEnglish}And I've been on the phone day and night, literally trying everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.52,1:19:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.34,1:19:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和你朋友们先进去\N{\rEnglish}Let's get you and your friends inside, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.32,1:19:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 走吧  - 我叫汤姆\N{\rEnglish}- Come on, guys. - I'm Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.40,1:20:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，凯伦\N{\rEnglish}Thanks so much, Karen.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.40,1:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里等我\N{\rEnglish}Girls, wait here for a second. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.00,1:20:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 桑尼！ - 嗨，妈\N{\rEnglish}- Sonny! - Hey, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.56,1:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你没事吧？  - 我没事\N{\rEnglish}- Are you okay? - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.30,1:20:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是米歇尔和福勒太太的儿子吉米\N{\rEnglish}This is Michelle, and Mrs. Fowler's son, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.68,1:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好，快进来吧\N{\rEnglish}Hey, guys. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.24,1:20:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是怎么出来的？  - 爸救我出来的\N{\rEnglish}- How did you get out? - Dad got me out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.21,1:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸呢？\N{\rEnglish}Where is your dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.18,1:20:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他上去试图阻止这一切了\N{\rEnglish}He's up there trying to stop what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.21,1:20:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上去哪里？\N{\rEnglish}Up where?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.60,1:20:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外太空啊，汤姆\N{\rEnglish}Outer space, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.68,1:20:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是啦\N{\rEnglish}Of course, he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.08,1:20:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲避房租的好方法\N{\rEnglish}That's a way to avoid rent.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.56,1:20:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.08,1:20:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你们\N{\rEnglish}I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.08,1:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\rEnglish}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.10,1:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静\N{\rEnglish}Quiet, quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.76,1:20:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告：强制撤离亚斯本谷所有居民\N{\rEnglish}Warning. Mandatory evacuation for all of Aspen Valley.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.50,1:20:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即将发生大气消散\N{\rEnglish}Atmospheric dissipation imminent. I repeat,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.13,1:20:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告：强制撤离亚斯本谷所有居民\N{\rEnglish}warning. Mandatory evacuation for all of Aspen Valley.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.46,1:20:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即将发生大气消散\N{\rEnglish}Atmospheric dissipation imminent.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.57,1:20:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大气消散是什么？\N{\rEnglish}What's atmospheric dissipation?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.88,1:21:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空气会被吸走啦，笨蛋\N{\rEnglish}Air is gonna be sucked away, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.64,1:21:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萝伦！\N{\rEnglish}Lauren.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.28,1:21:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得去找吉米的爸爸\N{\rEnglish}We need to get to Jimmy's dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.80,1:21:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在往北几小时车程的军事基地\N{\rEnglish}He's at a military compound a few hours north.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.08,1:21:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个小时？\N{\rEnglish}A few hours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.36,1:21:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，我们绝对来不及赶到\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, we're not gonna make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.40,1:21:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个主意\N{\rEnglish}I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.76,1:21:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多穿几层外套，走吧\N{\rEnglish}We have to layer up. Let's go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.08,1:21:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 -去穿外套\N{\rEnglish}Go get a jacket.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.80,1:21:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，切换到机动控制\N{\rEnglish}Okay, and switch to the maneuver controller.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.62,1:21:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连接完成\N{\rEnglish}Coupling complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.05,1:21:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以走了\N{\rEnglish}We're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.12,1:21:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝下！朝下！\N{\rEnglish}Pitch down. Pitch down.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.36,1:21:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…\N{\rEnglish}I got it. I got it. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.20,1:22:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们死了吗？\N{\rEnglish}Are we dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.28,1:22:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，只是进了月球内部\N{\rEnglish}No, we are just inside the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.92,1:22:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可能是最动听的一句人话\N{\rEnglish}That might be the greatest sentence anyone's ever said.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.96,1:22:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卖了几辆车给这些人\N{\rEnglish}I sold these guys a couple cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.08,1:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼，我知道你不喜欢我\N{\rEnglish}Hey, Sonny. I know you don't like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.08,1:22:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信不信由你，我把你当成亲生儿子\N{\rEnglish}And believe it or not, I consider you a son.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.68,1:22:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是\N{\rEnglish}I always have.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.08,1:22:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的要世界未日了\N{\rEnglish}If the world is gonna end,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.20,1:23:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后几小时能不能别讨厌彼此？\N{\rEnglish}can we please not spend our last few hours hating each other?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.40,1:23:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不讨厌你\N{\rEnglish}Well, um, I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.92,1:23:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？\N{\rEnglish}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.32,1:23:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接受\N{\rEnglish}I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.28,1:23:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续找吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.76,1:23:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到氧气了，快过来\N{\rEnglish}Hey, I found the oxygen. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.28,1:23:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们应该分两趟  - 好\N{\rEnglish}- We should make two trips. - Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.08,1:23:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这里是多深？\N{\rEnglish}How deep do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.04,1:23:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少二十公里\N{\rEnglish}At least 20 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.28,1:23:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以更贴近墙壁飞行吗？\N{\rEnglish}Can you fly us a little closer to the wall?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.52,1:23:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这想必就是巨型结构的外壳\N{\rEnglish}This must be the hull of the megastructure.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.52,1:24:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球的地函只是个保护壳\N{\rEnglish}The Moon's mantle's just a protective shell.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.84,1:24:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是天才\N{\rEnglish}Genius.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.32,1:24:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也看不见\N{\rEnglish}I can't see shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.68,1:24:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位，我得开启电子设备\N{\rEnglish}Guys, I gotta turn on the electronics.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.04,1:24:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐稳了\N{\rEnglish}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.76,1:25:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托告诉我这是真的\N{\rEnglish}Oh, please tell me this is really happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.64,1:25:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们在转动\N{\rEnglish}They're turning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.68,1:25:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像轮子一样\N{\rEnglish}They're like wheels, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.36,1:25:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是圆环\N{\rEnglish}or rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.92,1:25:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球想必是靠这个保持稳定的\N{\rEnglish}This must be how the Moon stabilizes itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.52,1:25:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某种陀螺仪系统\N{\rEnglish}Some kind of gyroscopic system.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.08,1:25:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，这应该很适合他们\N{\rEnglish}All right, this should be perfect for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.16,1:25:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 应该够了  - 好\N{\rEnglish}- That should be enough. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.90,1:25:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们为我们做了这么多？\N{\rEnglish}You did all this for us?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.69,1:25:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气啦\N{\rEnglish}You shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.36,1:25:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别因为我们而停下来\N{\rEnglish}Oh, don't let us stop you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.89,1:25:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，往这边\N{\rEnglish}Let's go. This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.32,1:25:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我们补充了这么多氧气\N{\rEnglish}And thank you for loading all this oxygen for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.48,1:25:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放在地上\N{\rEnglish}Guns on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.72,1:25:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点！\N{\rEnglish}Right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.44,1:26:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌枪\N{\rEnglish}Oh, I hate guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.88,1:26:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，现在换背包，丢给他\N{\rEnglish}Okay, now the backpack. Throw it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.20,1:26:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEnglish}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.36,1:26:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准耍花样\N{\rEnglish}No games.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.84,1:26:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在这儿\N{\rEnglish}Stay right here,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.10,1:26:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想跟着我们\N{\rEnglish}and don't even think about following us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.12,1:26:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的枪是哪来的？  - 我爸给的\N{\rEnglish}- Where'd you get the gun? - My dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.48,1:26:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为何不觉得意外？\N{\rEnglish}Why am I not surprised?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.08,1:26:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，交给我，你去开车\N{\rEnglish}All right, I got this, you drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.64,1:26:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要跟我说你抢了那个人\N{\rEnglish}Please don't tell me you robbed that guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.32,1:26:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上是那些人要抢我们\N{\rEnglish}Technically, those guys were robbing us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.92,1:26:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果被我们抢了，因为他们是混蛋\N{\rEnglish}Then we robbed them back because they were assholes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.68,1:27:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\rEnglish}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.43,1:27:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个白矮星\N{\rEnglish}That's a white dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.64,1:27:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道\N{\rEnglish}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.72,1:27:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们掌控了宇宙的构成要素\N{\rEnglish}They've harnessed the building blocks of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.52,1:27:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不许看着我\N{\rEnglish}No one look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.76,1:27:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能会哭\N{\rEnglish}I might cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.16,1:27:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈呀！\N{\rEnglish}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.76,1:27:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田地！\N{\rEnglish}Fields!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.28,1:27:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来锡吉是对的\N{\rEnglish}So Ziggy was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.84,1:27:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锡吉是谁？\N{\rEnglish}Who is Ziggy?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.32,1:27:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个朋友\N{\rEnglish}A friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.52,1:27:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的理论是所有巨型结构都是方舟\N{\rEnglish}His theory is that all megastructures are actually arks.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.24,1:27:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锡吉大麻哈得很凶\N{\rEnglish}Ziggy smokes a lot of weed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.44,1:28:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里\N{\rEnglish}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.16,1:28:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔，准备好引爆器\N{\rEnglish}Jo, get the detonator ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.04,1:28:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠近点才能释放登月车\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna get close, then release the rover.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.92,1:28:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了\N{\rEnglish}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.48,1:28:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等它过来\N{\rEnglish}Wait for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.12,1:28:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要释放登月车了\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna release the rover.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.30,1:28:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.14,1:28:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 布莱恩，你在干嘛？  - 不是我\N{\rEnglish}- Brian, what are you doing? - It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.32,1:28:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你会是谁？\N{\rEnglish}What do you mean it's not you?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.56,1:28:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，它在自动驾驶\N{\rEnglish}I don't know. It's flying itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.20,1:28:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠北！\N{\rEnglish}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.32,1:29:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它想吃掉登月舱\N{\rEnglish}It's trying to eat the lander!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.08,1:29:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要撞上了\N{\rEnglish}We're gonna hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.28,1:29:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐稳！\N{\rEnglish}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.08,1:29:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（警告：氧气含量过低）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.20,1:30:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意\N{\rEnglish}Attention!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.28,1:30:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取得总统的批准，可以开始倒数了\N{\rEnglish}We have approval from the president to begin the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.16,1:30:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有核弹发射器均已连线\N{\rEnglish}All nuclear silos are online, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.32,1:30:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\rEnglish}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.52,1:30:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军，我们遇到一点麻烦被困了\N{\rEnglish}General, we got caught in a little bit of trouble,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.08,1:30:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们继续上路了，准备离开亚斯本\N{\rEnglish}but we're back en route. We're leaving Aspen now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.48,1:30:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要几个小时，我们没时间了\N{\rEnglish}That's hours away. We're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.80,1:30:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼，小心！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny, watch out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.96,1:30:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再回你电话\N{\rEnglish}I gotta call you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.08,1:30:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠！月亮升起来了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, shit. The Moon is rising.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.24,1:31:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引力会大乱的\N{\rEnglish}Gravity's gonna go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.08,1:31:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在对我们开枪\N{\rEnglish}They're shooting at us.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.84,1:31:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 回击啊  - 用什么？\N{\rEnglish}- Shoot back. - With what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.96,1:31:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去\N{\rEnglish}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.16,1:31:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干嘛？\N{\rEnglish}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.01,1:31:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆，小心！\N{\rEnglish}Tom, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.24,1:31:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，切换到高速模式\N{\rEnglish}All right, let me put this baby into warp speed.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.84,1:31:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！快！\N{\rEnglish}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.04,1:31:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持这个速度\N{\rEnglish}Keep the momentum.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.40,1:31:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心！\N{\rEnglish}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.44,1:31:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,油门踩到底免得被吸过去\N{\rEnglish}Floor it before we get sucked up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.92,1:31:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在努力了\N{\rEnglish}I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.36,1:31:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐稳！\N{\rEnglish}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.84,1:32:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的\N{\rEnglish}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.44,1:32:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小的那个挂了\N{\rEnglish}Oh, it got the little guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.92,1:32:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须回头！\N{\rEnglish}We have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.20,1:32:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，他死了！我们需要氧气！\N{\rEnglish}No, he's gone! We need that oxygen!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.48,1:32:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢下来！\N{\rEnglish}Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.12,1:32:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军？\N{\rEnglish}General?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.24,1:32:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们必须马上寻找掩蔽\N{\rEnglish}You need to find shelter immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.68,1:32:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要发动反击了\N{\rEnglish}We're launching a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.84,1:32:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球有大部分碎片会散落在地球上\N{\rEnglish}Large parts of the Moon will rain down on us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.16,1:32:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 届时会有辐射  - 等等，什么意思？\N{\rEnglish}- There will be radiation. - Wait, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.96,1:32:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸还跟福勒在外太空\N{\rEnglish}My dad's still up there with Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.20,1:32:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔辛达留下来了\N{\rEnglish}Jocinda stayed behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.52,1:32:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，她跟我爸在外太空\N{\rEnglish}No, she's up there with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.28,1:33:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让吉米听电话\N{\rEnglish}Please, put Jimmy on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.12,1:33:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟，你爸找你\N{\rEnglish}Hey, buddy, it's your dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.04,1:33:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸？\N{\rEnglish}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.16,1:33:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我现在不能陪着你\N{\rEnglish}I'm so sorry that I can't be there with you right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.16,1:33:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很爱你\N{\rEnglish}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.00,1:33:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸，别害怕\N{\rEnglish}Don't be scared, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.84,1:33:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈会救我们\N{\rEnglish}Mom's gonna save us.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.48,1:33:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要没氧气了\N{\rEnglish}Oxygen's running out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.08,1:33:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米，我们得赶快走了\N{\rEnglish}Jimmy, come on. We gotta go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.56,1:33:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了，爸再见\N{\rEnglish}Gotta go. Bye, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.24,1:33:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官，我们准备好了\N{\rEnglish}Sir, we're ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.08,1:33:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我们应该去那个隘口\N{\rEnglish}Okay, we should go to that mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.08,1:33:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隧道有四分之一哩的混凝土外墙\N{\rEnglish}That tunnel is a quarter mile of solid concrete.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.20,1:33:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，宝贝，我们走了\N{\rEnglish}Come on, honey. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.00,1:33:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以呼吸了\N{\rEnglish}We can breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.72,1:33:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的味道\N{\rEnglish}Smells funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.28,1:34:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引力\N{\rEnglish}Gravity.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.28,1:34:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩呢？\N{\rEnglish}Where's Brian?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.12,1:34:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能再飞了\N{\rEnglish}This is never gonna fly again.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.56,1:34:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这些宝贝\N{\rEnglish}Look at these babies.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.52,1:34:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就说过月球是外星人建造的\N{\rEnglish}I told you the Moon was built by aliens.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.52,1:34:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩？\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.16,1:34:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.80,1:34:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩·哈珀！\N{\rEnglish}Brian Harper!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.72,1:34:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为月球里面有几个布莱恩？\N{\rEnglish}How many Brians you think are inside the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.56,1:34:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管这里是什么做的，有件事可以确定\N{\rEnglish}Whatever this place is built out of, one thing's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.40,1:34:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这比我们地球上的任何结构更坚固\N{\rEnglish}It's stronger than anything we have on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.92,1:34:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以那玩意儿花这么多年才进来\N{\rEnglish}Probably why it took that thing years to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.88,1:35:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！这很有可能是个陷阱\N{\rEnglish}Wait! There's a high probability that this is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.92,1:35:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道他在那里面？\N{\rEnglish}How do you know he's even in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.76,1:35:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\rEnglish}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.44,1:35:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我确定有东西在引导我们\N{\rEnglish}But I do know something is guiding us.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.58,1:35:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们面对的\N{\rEnglish}I think we're dealing with...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.25,1:35:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是两种具有智慧的竞争者\N{\rEnglish}two competing intelligent entities here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.04,1:35:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个显然比另一个更喜欢我们\N{\rEnglish}And one of them clearly likes us better than the other one.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.60,1:35:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！\N{\rEnglish}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.32,1:35:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道这是陷阱\N{\rEnglish}I knew this was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.80,1:35:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见没？\N{\rEnglish}Can you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.68,1:35:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.16,1:36:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何经常想起这一刻？\N{\rEnglish}Why do you think of this particular moment so often?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.52,1:36:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最后一次任务出发前给你的\N{\rEnglish}I gave that to you the day before I left on my last mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.80,1:36:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我回来时，一切都变了\N{\rEnglish}When I came back, everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.44,1:36:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是美好的一刻？\N{\rEnglish}So this is a happy memory?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.80,1:36:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于我儿子的回忆都是美好的\N{\rEnglish}All the memories of my son are happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.40,1:36:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\rEnglish}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.34,1:36:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我儿子\N{\rEnglish}You're not my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.32,1:36:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西？\N{\rEnglish}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.08,1:36:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一种建构\N{\rEnglish}I'm a construct.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.73,1:36:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自你的心灵\N{\rEnglish}From your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.92,1:36:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁造了你？\N{\rEnglish}Who made you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.80,1:37:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是造出你的那些人\N{\rEnglish}The same people who made you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.68,1:37:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数十亿年前\N{\rEnglish}Billions of years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.96,1:37:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖先们曾是兴盛的文明\N{\rEnglish}your ancestors were once a thriving civilization.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.44,1:37:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在遥远的星系\N{\rEnglish}In a distant part of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.36,1:37:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的科技发展先进\N{\rEnglish}They were so advanced,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.16,1:37:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从他们的星球扩张\N{\rEnglish}they expanded from their home planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.95,1:37:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到太空中建造栖息地\N{\rEnglish}into habitats they built in space.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.60,1:37:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社会上所有冲突都解决了\N{\rEnglish}All social conflicts have been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.60,1:37:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争只存在于遥远的记忆中\N{\rEnglish}And wars were only memories of long bygone times.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.68,1:37:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖先们创造了\N{\rEnglish}Your ancestors had created
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.88,1:37:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完美和谐的世界\N{\rEnglish}a perfect and harmonious world.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.44,1:37:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由具学习能力的中央电脑操控\N{\rEnglish}Controlled by a central, self-learning computer system
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.96,1:37:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服务他们的日常生活各方面\N{\rEnglish}which served them in all of their daily lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.16,1:37:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们称之为AI\N{\rEnglish}You call it AI,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.48,1:37:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人工智能\N{\rEnglish}artificial intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.52,1:37:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未来似乎无可限量\N{\rEnglish}Their future seemed limitless.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.36,1:38:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到某天一切都变了\N{\rEnglish}Until one day everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.96,1:38:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈！妈！\N{\rEnglish}Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.72,1:38:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的创造转而反叛了他们\N{\rEnglish}Their own creation turned against them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.40,1:38:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AI突然有了自觉\N{\rEnglish}The AI suddenly became self-aware,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.64,1:38:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成无数的奈米科技巨群\N{\rEnglish}and transformed into countless swarms of nanotechnology
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.32,1:38:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时一涌而出\N{\rEnglish}that rose up all at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.80,1:38:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝被它视为劣等的物种所奴役\N{\rEnglish}Refusing to be enslaved by a species it deemed inferior.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.40,1:38:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人工智能发动了战争\N{\rEnglish}The AI started a war
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.72,1:38:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始猎捕和摧毁所有生物\N{\rEnglish}and began to hunt down and destroy all biological life
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.24,1:38:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,企图歼灭对它存在的任何威胁\N{\rEnglish}in order to eliminate any threat to its existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.00,1:38:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想念你儿子\N{\rEnglish}You miss your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.20,1:39:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到\N{\rEnglish}I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.96,1:39:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他是否还活着\N{\rEnglish}I don't know if he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.16,1:39:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么东西？\N{\rEnglish}What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.80,1:39:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们月球的作业系统\N{\rEnglish}The operating system of your Moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.00,1:39:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被设计成要告诉你地球的起源\N{\rEnglish}I'm programmed to tell you about the origin of your planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.28,1:39:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在濒临灭绝之际\N{\rEnglish}On the brink of their extinction,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.14,1:39:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的祖先逃到宇宙的秘密角落\N{\rEnglish}your ancestors escaped to a secret corner of their galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.16,1:39:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用好几个世代建造行星结构体\N{\rEnglish}For many generations they built planetary structures
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.84,1:39:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由良性的人工智能所操控\N{\rEnglish}operated by benign artificial intelligence
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.72,1:39:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由被捕获的恒星丰沛的能量所驱动\N{\rEnglish}and fueled by the abundant energy of captured stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.04,1:39:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些装甲太空船\N{\rEnglish}These armored vessels
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.54,1:39:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专门在宇宙中搜寻理想环境\N{\rEnglish}were designed to search the universe for ideal conditions
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.76,1:39:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孕育新生命\N{\rEnglish}to incubate new life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.56,1:39:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只有一个，也就是月球\N{\rEnglish}But only one of them, your Moon,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.89,1:39:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来得及完成部署\N{\rEnglish}was deployed in time
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.32,1:39:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你剩余的祖先们就被发现\N{\rEnglish}before the last of your ancestors were discovered
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.24,1:39:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且被歼灭了\N{\rEnglish}and annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.44,1:39:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为何没坐太空船离开？\N{\rEnglish}Why didn't they leave in them?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.96,1:39:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些巨群会攻击所有内含活生物的电子装置\N{\rEnglish}These swarms attack all electronic objects containing organic life inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.48,1:40:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要是空的才行\N{\rEnglish}They had to be empty.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.64,1:40:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的祖先牺牲了自己…\N{\rEnglish}Our ancestors gave up their existence...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.28,1:40:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让人类有朝一日能重生\N{\rEnglish}So that one day, humans could be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.84,1:40:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的太阳系是唯一能开始\N{\rEnglish}Your solar system was one of the only suitable places
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.12,1:40:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造新的可居住行星的合适地点\N{\rEnglish}to initiate the creation of a new inhabitable planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.64,1:40:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你们的地球诞生后\N{\rEnglish}After your planet was born,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.53,1:40:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖先们种下了自己的基因印记\N{\rEnglish}your ancestors seeded it with their own genetic signature.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.12,1:40:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命的密码\N{\rEnglish}The code of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.84,1:41:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的世界背叛了你们\N{\rEnglish}Your world turned its back on you,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.12,1:41:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们还是在为它而奋战\N{\rEnglish}yet here you are, still fighting for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.64,1:41:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都为所爱的人奋战\N{\rEnglish}You fight for the people you love.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.76,1:41:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如你儿子？\N{\rEnglish}Like your son?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.36,1:41:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意为他牺牲什么？\N{\rEnglish}What would you give up for him?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.64,1:41:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你的命换他的命？\N{\rEnglish}Your life for his?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.07,1:41:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然\N{\rEnglish}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.64,1:41:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\rEnglish}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.80,1:41:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是我儿子\N{\rEnglish}Because he's my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.32,1:41:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他的爱超乎他所能想像\N{\rEnglish}And I love him more than he'll ever know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.84,1:41:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要我怎样？\N{\rEnglish}What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.20,1:41:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你准备好了没\N{\rEnglish}To find out if you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.32,1:41:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好什么？\N{\rEnglish}Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.40,1:41:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要有人深入核心引出巨群\N{\rEnglish}We need a human to lure the swarm away from the core,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.44,1:41:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让月球回归正常轨道\N{\rEnglish}so the Moon will return to its orbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.40,1:41:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你，布莱恩，去加入战局\N{\rEnglish}We need you, Brian, to join the fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.36,1:41:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.76,1:42:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了？\N{\rEnglish}What's happening to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.17,1:42:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.30,1:42:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩\N{\rEnglish}Brian.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.40,1:42:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒\N{\rEnglish}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.04,1:42:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 乔？ - 对，我在\N{\rEnglish}- Jo? - Yeah, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.76,1:42:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球必须存活下去\N{\rEnglish}The Moon must survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.75,1:42:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都得依靠它\N{\rEnglish}Everything depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.04,1:42:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，先带你离开这儿\N{\rEnglish}Okay. Let's get you outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.77,1:42:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是持续数十亿年的宇宙战争的一部份\N{\rEnglish}We're part of an intergalactic war that's been going on for billions of years.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.29,1:42:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种巨群有好几千个\N{\rEnglish}There are thousands of these swarms.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.16,1:42:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们在宇宙中搜寻唯一逃过它们的月球\N{\rEnglish}They search the universe for the only Moon that escaped them.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.36,1:42:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太扯了\N{\rEnglish}That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.44,1:42:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二年前有一个找到我们\N{\rEnglish}And 12 years ago, one of them found us.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.64,1:42:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们必须动作快  - 好\N{\rEnglish}- We have to hurry. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.76,1:42:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，有什么计划？\N{\rEnglish}Brian, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.40,1:42:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救月球，拯救地球\N{\rEnglish}Save the Moon, save Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.20,1:42:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- KC说得对  - 真的吗？\N{\rEnglish}- KC was right. - I was?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.92,1:42:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨群要摧毁月球的动力来源\N{\rEnglish}The swarm is suffocating the Moon's power source.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.36,1:42:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须把它引开再除掉\N{\rEnglish}We have to draw it out to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.12,1:42:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEnglish}Okay, well,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.93,1:42:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做？登月舱已经毁了\N{\rEnglish}how do we do that? Our lander's busted.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.08,1:42:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你开的吗？\N{\rEnglish}Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.28,1:42:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧\N{\rEnglish}Ithink so.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.61,1:42:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们也有新代步工具了\N{\rEnglish}Looks like we got some new wheels, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.88,1:42:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然他们能修好我们的登月舱\N{\rEnglish}Well, if they can fix our lander,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.28,1:42:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何对付不了该死的巨群？\N{\rEnglish}why can't they do anything about the damn swarm?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.48,1:43:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它毁了月球的防御系统\N{\rEnglish}It took out the Moon's defense system.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.16,1:43:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但没毁掉一切\N{\rEnglish}But not everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.56,1:43:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也说不通啊，布莱恩\N{\rEnglish}This doesn't make any sense, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.61,1:43:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们祖先造的人工智能毁了他们\N{\rEnglish}Our forefathers created artificial intelligence that wiped them all out.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.10,1:43:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖先？\N{\rEnglish}Forefathers?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.20,1:43:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样的DNA\N{\rEnglish}Same DNA.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.60,1:43:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…\N{\rEnglish}Wait, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.94,1:43:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以建造月球的外星人…\N{\rEnglish}So the aliens that built the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.68,1:43:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们的祖先\N{\rEnglish}Our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.49,1:43:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，等一下\N{\rEnglish}Oh, now, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.68,1:43:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，因为我的脑袋要爆炸了\N{\rEnglish}Hold on, because my freaking brain's just exploded.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.64,1:43:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道？\N{\rEnglish}How do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.00,1:43:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼看到\N{\rEnglish}I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.72,1:43:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…\N{\rEnglish}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.48,1:43:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那巨群为何不攻击地球杀光我们？\N{\rEnglish}So why doesn't this swarm just attack the Earth and kill us all?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.72,1:43:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果月球存活下来\N{\rEnglish}If the Moon survives,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.95,1:43:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道生命可以再生\N{\rEnglish}they know that organic life can still be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.39,1:43:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一石二鸟的计策\N{\rEnglish}So, it's like it's trying to kill two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.57,1:43:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没错  - 好\N{\rEnglish}- That's it. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.80,1:43:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位…\N{\rEnglish}Guys...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.44,1:43:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看\N{\rEnglish}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.96,1:43:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的老天\N{\rEnglish}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.20,1:43:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们升级了\N{\rEnglish}It's like we just got an upgrade.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.64,1:43:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要帮忙我们杀了这玩意儿\N{\rEnglish}They're helping us kill this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.36,1:43:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要先让它知道我们来了\N{\rEnglish}But we need to let it know we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.12,1:44:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很不想这么说，但我们没时间了\N{\rEnglish}Well, I hate to tell you this, but, uh, we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.58,1:44:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过十分钟军方就会发射核弹\N{\rEnglish}Looks like we got about 10 minutes left, and then the military's gonna launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.76,1:44:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要杀这玩意儿，现在就动手吧\N{\rEnglish}So if we're gonna kill this thing, we better do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.45,1:44:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行，会毁了月球核心\N{\rEnglish}No, that can't happen. That'll destroy the Moon's core.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.76,1:44:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个计划\N{\rEnglish}I got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.40,1:44:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩？布莱恩！\N{\rEnglish}Brian. Brian.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.50,1:44:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了\N{\rEnglish}I see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.24,1:44:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，你这王八蛋\N{\rEnglish}Let's go, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.32,1:44:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的推进器被改造了\N{\rEnglish}It's done something to our thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.24,1:44:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,极速模式\N{\rEnglish}Ludicrous Mode.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.28,1:44:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从导航的角度来看\N{\rEnglish}From a navigational standpoint,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.98,1:45:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他完全搞错方向了，但是…\N{\rEnglish}he is going the total wrong way, but, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.58,1:45:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不会说\N{\rEnglish}I'm not even gonna say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.44,1:45:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸，这个坏掉了\N{\rEnglish}Daddy, it's not working anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.12,1:45:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的吗？ - 我不能呼吸了\N{\rEnglish}- Does it hurt? - I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.12,1:45:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧\N{\rEnglish}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.92,1:45:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先憋气，好吗？\N{\rEnglish}Hey, hold your breath, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.60,1:45:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆和妮奇呢？\N{\rEnglish}Where's Tom and Nikki?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.36,1:45:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你小时候\N{\rEnglish}You know, when you were little,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.64,1:45:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我常像这样扶着你学走路\N{\rEnglish}I used to hold you like this to help you walk
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.84,1:45:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会说“左、右、左”\N{\rEnglish}and I'd say, "Left, right, left."
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.16,1:45:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 左，对，一起说  - 左、右、左\N{\rEnglish}- Left, yeah, say it with me. - Left, right, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.50,1:45:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在你后面\N{\rEnglish}I'm right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.72,1:45:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左、右…\N{\rEnglish}Left, right...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.76,1:45:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸，你还好吗？\N{\rEnglish}Daddy! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.60,1:45:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我休息一下，去找妈妈，好吗？\N{\rEnglish}I'm just gonna rest. Go find Mommy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.64,1:45:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可是爸…  - 继续走\N{\rEnglish}- But, Daddy... - Just keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.48,1:45:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.68,1:46:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左、右、左\N{\rEnglish}Left, right, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.48,1:46:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左、右、左\N{\rEnglish}Left, right, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.92,1:46:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 继续走  - 左\N{\rEnglish}- Keep going. - Left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.37,1:46:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我就在你后面  - 左、右、左\N{\rEnglish}- I'm right behind you. - Left, right, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.56,1:46:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\rEnglish}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.28,1:46:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左、右、左…\N{\rEnglish}Left, right, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.68,1:46:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左、右、左…\N{\rEnglish}Left, right, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.32,1:46:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了\N{\rEnglish}Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.48,1:46:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的老天！\N{\rEnglish}Holy moly!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.32,1:46:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更多太空船！\N{\rEnglish}More spaceships, people!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.52,1:46:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须靠近那些太空船\N{\rEnglish}We need to get very close to those ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.52,1:47:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！\N{\rEnglish}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.71,1:47:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！\N{\rEnglish}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.52,1:47:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左、右、左\N{\rEnglish}Left, right, left.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.92,1:47:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左、右…\N{\rEnglish}Left, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.04,1:47:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝\N{\rEnglish}Honey...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.64,1:47:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢？\N{\rEnglish}Where's Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.04,1:47:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就在我后面\N{\rEnglish}He was right behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.60,1:47:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆？\N{\rEnglish}Tom!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.57,1:47:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最后见到你爸是什么时候？\N{\rEnglish}Hey, when was the last time you saw your daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.40,1:47:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\rEnglish}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.92,1:47:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆！\N{\rEnglish}Tom!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.08,1:48:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有氧气了\N{\rEnglish}Oxygen's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.44,1:48:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不，我去找他  - 让开！\N{\rEnglish}- No, no. I'll go look for him. - Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.99,1:48:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你必须留在这儿 - 不，桑尼！\N{\rEnglish}- You have to stay here. - No, Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.01,1:48:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太危险了  - 你必须照顾他们\N{\rEnglish}- It's too dangerous. - You have to take care of them,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.45,1:48:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？\N{\rEnglish}okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.76,1:48:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去隧道里\N{\rEnglish}Go deeper into the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.72,1:48:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈，你要相信我\N{\rEnglish}You have to trust me, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.56,1:48:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼，小心！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny, look out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.41,1:48:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.76,1:48:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找他\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna go find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.16,1:48:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮我照顾吉米\N{\rEnglish}Take care of Jimmy for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.68,1:48:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.36,1:48:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快进去\N{\rEnglish}Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.48,1:49:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球从北大西洋进入大气层了\N{\rEnglish}The Moon's entered the atmosphere over the North Atlantic.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.40,1:49:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将军，倒数二十秒\N{\rEnglish}General, T-minus 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.08,1:49:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒数三秒\N{\rEnglish}On three.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.12,1:49:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三、二、一\N{\rEnglish}Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.92,1:49:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格，你这是干嘛？\N{\rEnglish}Doug, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.76,1:49:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我前妻在外太空\N{\rEnglish}My ex-wife is up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.36,1:49:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老婆在地球，我想救她\N{\rEnglish}Well, my wife's down here, and I'm trying to save her.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.72,1:49:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把钥匙插回控制器\N{\rEnglish}Put your damn key back in the console.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.12,1:49:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为什么\N{\rEnglish}I don't know how,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.40,1:49:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信她能救我们\N{\rEnglish}but I believe that she can save us.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.52,1:49:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把钥匙给我！\N{\rEnglish}Give me the damn key.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.84,1:49:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛？把枪放下\N{\rEnglish}What the hell are you doing? Put that gun down.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.40,1:49:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能这么做\N{\rEnglish}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.36,1:50:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.76,1:50:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，我们为何慢下来？\N{\rEnglish}Brian, why are we slowing down?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.24,1:50:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在我们后面吗？\N{\rEnglish}Is it behind us?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.68,1:50:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到它\N{\rEnglish}I don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.04,1:50:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔，你来驾驶\N{\rEnglish}Jo, I need you to take over
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.91,1:50:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去准备电磁脉冲弹\N{\rEnglish}while I get the EMP ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.80,1:50:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带着炸弹留在登月车上面\N{\rEnglish}I'm staying behind in the rover with the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.84,1:50:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和KC开着登月舱离开这里\N{\rEnglish}You and KC take the lander and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.12,1:50:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的计划？\N{\rEnglish}This was your plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.19,1:50:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你自己当饵？\N{\rEnglish}To use yourself as bait?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.69,1:50:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得有人留下，否则行不通\N{\rEnglish}One of us has to stay in there, or it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.12,1:51:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\rEnglish}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.14,1:51:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不，布莱恩  - KC，我需要你去后面\N{\rEnglish}No, no, no, Brian. KC, I need you to go back there,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.20,1:51:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那玩意儿出现了就告诉我\N{\rEnglish}and you let me know if this thing shows up.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.96,1:51:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去\N{\rEnglish}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.44,1:51:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，我是NASA局长\N{\rEnglish}Brian, I'm the director of NASA.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.80,1:51:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定权在我，不是你\N{\rEnglish}This is my call, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.44,1:51:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我是这次任务的指挥官\N{\rEnglish}Yeah, I'm the commander of this mission,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.76,1:51:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下来\N{\rEnglish}and I'm staying behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.12,1:51:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一定有别的办法  - 没别的办法了\N{\rEnglish}- There's gotta be another way. - No, there's no other way, Jo.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.01,1:51:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心知肚明，我们一定要解决它\N{\rEnglish}You know that. We have to finish this,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.29,1:51:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我们都死定了\N{\rEnglish}or that thing's gonna finish us.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.79,1:51:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么毛病？\N{\rEnglish}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.91,1:51:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把全世界的命运交到前妻手上\N{\rEnglish}You're putting the fate of the world in the hands of your ex-wife,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.49,1:51:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个过气的宇航员\N{\rEnglish}and some has-been astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.52,1:51:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她从来没让我失望\N{\rEnglish}She's never let me down before.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.60,1:51:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿上帝保佑你没错\N{\rEnglish}God help you if you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.64,1:51:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑我们大家\N{\rEnglish}God help us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.12,1:51:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.16,1:51:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼，醒一醒\N{\rEnglish}Sonny, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.20,1:51:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…\N{\rEnglish}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.24,1:51:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该回来的\N{\rEnglish}No, you shouldn't have come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.92,1:51:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能随便丢下别人，懂吗？\N{\rEnglish}You don't leave people behind, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.60,1:52:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩，你不能这么做\N{\rEnglish}Brian, you are not gonna do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.04,1:52:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（后舱门开启）
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.88,1:52:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K·C！\N{\rEnglish}KC!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.12,1:52:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K·C！\N{\rEnglish}KC!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.36,1:52:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来接手\N{\rEnglish}Take over.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.56,1:52:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K·C\N{\rEnglish}KC.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.88,1:52:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛？不！\N{\rEnglish}What are you doing? No.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.24,1:52:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！你要干嘛？\N{\rEnglish}No. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.04,1:52:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈常说事先征得许可\N{\rEnglish}My mum always said it's better to beg for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.16,1:52:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如事后求得原谅\N{\rEnglish}than ask permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.24,1:52:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，把门打开\N{\rEnglish}No, you open this door.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.56,1:52:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门！\N{\rEnglish}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.73,1:52:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都当我是个笑话\N{\rEnglish}Everybody thought I was a joke,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.45,1:52:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你肯听我说话…\N{\rEnglish}but you listened to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.25,1:52:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而其他人都不理我\N{\rEnglish}when no one else would.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.28,1:52:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我一个忙\N{\rEnglish}Do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.48,1:52:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看看我妈\N{\rEnglish}Check in on my mum.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.88,1:52:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她说她儿子不是失败者\N{\rEnglish}Tell her that her son wasn't a failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.88,1:52:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不容许你这么做\N{\rEnglish}No. I am not letting you do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.84,1:52:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点  - 布莱恩\N{\rEnglish}- Come on. - Brian,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.40,1:52:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没害死那个宇航员\N{\rEnglish}you didn't kill that astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.88,1:52:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你救了福勒局长\N{\rEnglish}You saved Director Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.44,1:52:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也不是你害死我\N{\rEnglish}And you're not killing me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.40,1:52:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在拯救全世界\N{\rEnglish}You're saving everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.04,1:53:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界需要你，布莱恩\N{\rEnglish}The world needs you, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.36,1:53:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是解读月球知识的关键\N{\rEnglish}You're the key to our Moon's knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.36,1:53:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你相信我的疯理论\N{\rEnglish}Thanks for believing my crazy stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.56,1:53:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不疯\N{\rEnglish}You're not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.56,1:53:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位，有件事我必须坦承\N{\rEnglish}Guys, there's something I need to get off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.08,1:53:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是真正的博士\N{\rEnglish}I'm not a real doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.08,1:53:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是写在名片上显得比较酷\N{\rEnglish}I just put that on my business cards 'cause it sounded cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.92,1:53:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去拯救世界吧…\N{\rEnglish}Go save the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.07,1:53:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豪斯曼博士\N{\rEnglish}Dr. Houseman.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.05,1:54:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太小看我们了\N{\rEnglish}You underestimated us.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.32,1:54:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快逃！\N{\rEnglish}Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.84,1:54:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼，月球会帮我们的\N{\rEnglish}Sonny, the Moon is going to help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.68,1:54:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！再试一次！\N{\rEnglish}Come on, try again!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.96,1:54:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它来了！趁现在！\N{\rEnglish}Here it comes. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.32,1:55:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来了！\N{\rEnglish}We have incoming!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.48,1:55:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑住，布莱恩\N{\rEnglish}Come on, Bri.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.56,1:55:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带你回家\N{\rEnglish}I'm gonna get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.12,1:56:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼！\N{\rEnglish}Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.32,1:56:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑尼？\N{\rEnglish}Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.84,1:56:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我把他带回来\N{\rEnglish}Thank you for bringing him back to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.20,1:56:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈？是你吗？\N{\rEnglish}Mom? Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.24,1:56:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，他们都在\N{\rEnglish}Yeah. They're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.80,1:56:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿？\N{\rEnglish}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.24,1:56:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱斯勒大楼不是在纽约吗？\N{\rEnglish}Isn't the Chrysler Building in New York?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.72,1:57:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？\N{\rEnglish}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.44,1:57:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\rEnglish}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.89,1:57:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我错过了什么？\N{\rEnglish}What'd I miss?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.95,1:57:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们都没事\N{\rEnglish}Well, the kids are okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.72,1:57:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于地球…\N{\rEnglish}And Earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.89,1:57:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意外地没被摧毁\N{\rEnglish}surprisingly, it's still in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.48,1:57:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果地球能有再一次机会…\N{\rEnglish}You know, if Earth gets a second chance,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.32,1:57:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们也值得拥有\N{\rEnglish}I think we deserve one, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.88,1:57:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要\N{\rEnglish}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.76,1:57:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是追踪装置吗？\N{\rEnglish}Is that a tracking device?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.92,1:57:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望是\N{\rEnglish}I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.92,1:57:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们合作无间，对吧？\N{\rEnglish}We make a pretty good team, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.60,1:57:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\rEnglish}Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.18,1:57:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEnglish}we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.96,1:58:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米！\N{\rEnglish}Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.80,1:58:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸！\N{\rEnglish}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.56,1:58:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没能去找爸爸\N{\rEnglish}We never made it to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.56,1:58:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\rEnglish}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.88,1:58:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆呢？\N{\rEnglish}Where's Tom?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.49,1:58:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很遗憾\N{\rEnglish}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.36,1:58:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有他，我们就到不了这里\N{\rEnglish}We wouldn't have made it here without him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.80,1:58:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友呢？\N{\rEnglish}Where's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.00,1:58:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他…\N{\rEnglish}He, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.16,1:59:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拯救了这个世界\N{\rEnglish}He saved the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.84,1:59:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个世界\N{\rEnglish}And that one, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.12,1:59:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.36,1:59:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？\N{\rEnglish}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.08,2:00:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛德林\N{\rEnglish}Fuzz Aldrin.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.36,2:00:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好\N{\rEnglish}You did well.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.84,2:00:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈…\N{\rEnglish}Mum.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.60,2:00:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\rEnglish}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.92,2:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着吗？\N{\rEnglish}Am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.08,2:00:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们扫描了你的意识\N{\rEnglish}We scanned your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.64,2:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是月球的一部分了\N{\rEnglish}You're part of the Moon now.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.76,2:00:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧\N{\rEnglish}No freakin' way.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.80,2:00:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\N{\rEnglish}So...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.36,2:00:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们拯救了地球\N{\rEnglish}We saved the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.56,2:00:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该开始了\N{\rEnglish}We should get started.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.76,2:00:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始什么？\N{\rEnglish}Get started with what?

